quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPressed%20for%20details%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20hearing%2C%20Grusch%20repeatedly%20said%20he%20could%20not%20comment%20in%20a%20public%20setting%20because%20the%20information%20is%20classified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20US%20government%20is%20hiding%20information%20on%20UAPs%20not%20only%20from%20the%20public%20but%20from%20Congress%2C%20and%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%20interviewed%26quot%3B%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20non-human%20craft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20testimony%20is%20based%20on%20information%20I've%20been%20given%20by%20individuals%20with%20a%20longstanding%20track%20record%20of%20legitimacy%20and%20service%20to%20this%20country%20--%20many%20of%20whom%20also%20shared%20compelling%20evidence%20in%20the%20form%20of%20photography%2C%20official%20documentation%2C%20and%20classified%20oral%20testimony%2C%26quot%3B%20Grusch%20told%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Representative%20Tim%20Burchett%20supported%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20government%20was%20concealing%20information%2C%20saying%20at%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20hearing%20--%20which%20also%20featured%20testimony%20from%20two%20former%20Navy%20officers%20who%20said%20they%20witnessed%20UAPs%20--%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20going%20to%20uncover%20the%20cover-up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20issue%20of%20government%20transparency.%20We%20can't%20trust%20a%20government%20that%20does%20not%20trust%20its%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Pentagon%20office%20set%20up%20to%20identify%20UAPs%20that%20pose%20a%20potential%20threat%20told%20lawmakers%20earlier%20this%20year%20it%20had%20not%20identified%20signs%20of%20alien%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20All-domain%20Anomaly%20Resolution%20Office%20%26quot%3Bhas%20found%20no%20credible%20evidence%20thus%20far%20of%20extraterrestrial%20activity%2C%20off-world%20technology%2C%20o