22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gmaddaus%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fwga-sag-aftra-no-negotiations-amptp-1235680241%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fwga-sag-aftra-no-negotiations-amptp-1235680241%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fwga-sag-aftra-no-negotiations-amptp-1235680241%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Not%20About%20Numbers%5C%22%3A%20What%20Opposition%20Wants%20From%20No-Confidence%20Motion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20itinerary%20for%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20will%20be%20discussed%20tomorrow%20between%20the%20Speaker%20and%20the%20political%20parties.%20The%20opposition%2C%20low%20on%20numbers%2C%20is%20not%20expecting%20to%20get%20the%20motion%20passed.%20Its%20only%20aim%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20is%20to%20get%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20speak%20on%20Manipur%20--%20a%20demand%20that%20the%20government%20has%20so%20far%20brushed%20off.%20The%20government%20is%20willing%20to%20allow%20only%20a%20discussion%20and%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20543-member%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20five%20seats%20are%20vacant%2C%20bringing%20down%20the%20majority%20mark%20to%20270.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20301%20seats%20including%20that%20of%20the%20Speaker%2C%20which%20vaults%20over%20the%20majority%20mark.%20The%20total%20NDA%20figure%20with%20allies%20reaches%20331.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20the%20'non-aligned%20parties'%20--%2010%20including%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20BSP%20and%20TDP%20--%20which%20can%20give%20indirect%20support%20to%20the%20government%20by%20remaining%20absent%20and%20thereby%20bringing%20down%20the%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20is%20trailing%20far%20behind.%20The%20total%20numbers%20the%20united%20opposition%20front%20can%20tote%20up%20is%20143.%20If%20smaller%20parties%20that%20are%20not%20siding%20with%20the%20BJP%20are%20included%2C%20the%20number%20reaches%20159.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20aware%20of%20how%20the%20land%20lies%2C%20has%20said%20the%20proposal%20was%20brought%20so%20that%20PM%20Modi%20could%20be%20forced%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20Manipur%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BINDIA%20alliance%20is%20aware%20of%20its%20numbers%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20but%20this%20is%20not%20just%20about%20numbers.%20This%20is%20about%20Manipur's%20fight%20for%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress's%20Gaurav%20Gogoi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20message%20should%20go%20out%20to%20the%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20of%20Manipur%20that%20PM%20Modi%20might%20have%20forgotten%20Manipur%20but%20INDIA%20alliance%20stands%20with%20them%20in%20this%20hour%20of%20grief%20and%20we%20are%20fighting%20for%20their%20rights%2C%20inside%20the%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20tell%20PM%20Modi%20to%20come%20to%20parliament%20and%20address%20the%20nation%20as%20this%20matter%20is%20not%20about%20Manipur%20alone%20anymore%20but%20it%20has%20spread%20over%20to%20other%20states%20as%20well.%20In%20the%20interest%20of%20national%20security%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20PM%20should%20address%20the%20country%20from%20inside%20parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETomorrow%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20will%20hold%20a%20discussion%20with%20leaders%20of%20all%20parties%20regarding%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20motion.%20Discussion%20will%20also%20be%20held%20on%20how%20much%20time%20each%20party%20will%20get%20to%20speak.%20Sources%20said%20the%20motion%20can%20be%20tabled%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20which%20started%20on%20July%2020%20and%20will%20c