%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Ffed-raises-interest-rates-leaves-door-open-to-another-hike%2Famp_articleshow%2F102148885.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Don't%20Interfere%5C%22%3A%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20After%20Mizoram%20Counterpart's%20Rally%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20asked%20his%20Mizoram%20counterpart%20Zoramthanga%20not%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20internal%20matters%20of%20another%20state%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Zoramthanga%20participated%20in%20a%20rally%20to%20show%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Kuki%20tribe%20in%20ethnic%20violence-hit%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mizoram%20government%20is%20sheltering%20about%2013%2C000%20internally%20displaced%20Kuki-Zo%20tribe%20people%20who%20fled%20from%20Manipur%20ever%20since%20the%20clashes%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203.%20The%20Mizo%20tribe%20has%20a%20strong%20connection%20with%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribe%20and%20Chin%20people%20of%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2031%2C000%20Chin%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%20are%20also%20being%20sheltered%20in%20Mizoram.%20They%20fled%20Myanmar%20after%20fierce%20fighting%20between%20the%20Myanmar%20army%20and%20resistance%20groups%20and%20ethnic%20rebel%20groups%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTension%20began%20when%20the%20state%20government%20started%20to%20act%20against%20drug%20cartels...%20The%20Manipur%20government%20is%20not%20against%20the%20Kuki%20community%20who%20are%20living%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20at%20an%20event%20to%20mark%20the%20Kargil%20Vijay%20Diwas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganisations%20representing%20the%20Kukis%20have%20been%20accusing%20the%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20working%20against%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20tribe%2C%20who%20are%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20while%20the%20Meiteis%20are%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20his%20government%20has%20been%20tracking%20all%20the%20incidents%20that%20have%20been%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20and%20warned%20against%20those%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20destroy%20the%20integrity%20of%20Manipur%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20fight%20is%20between%20the%20government%20and%20elements%20%26quot%3Bwho%20want%20to%20disturb%20peaceful%20co-existence%20in%20the%20state%26quot%3B.%20He%20termed%20as%20%26quot%3Bbarbaric%26quot%3B%20the%20way%20rally%20participants%20with%20Zoramthanga%20in%20Mizoram's%20capital%20Aizawl%20shouted%20abusive%20slogans%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ask%20the%20Mizoram%20chief%20minister%20not%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20internal%20matter%20of%20another%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20criticised%20the%20European%20Parliament%2C%20which%20without%20knowing%20the%20ground%20reality%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20on%20July%2013%20asking%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20protect%20religious%20minorities%2C%20when%20the%20crisis%20in%20Manipur%20is%20not%20linked%20to%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20the%20state%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20driving%20out%20illegal%20migrants%20and%20rejected%20the%20demand%20by%20Kukis%20of%20a%20separate%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meiteis%20have%20alleged%20the%20violence%20that%20began%20on%20May%203%20over%20the%20Meiteis'%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20status%20was%20only%20an%20excuse%20for%20the%20Kukis%20to%20start%20a%20major%20conflict%20so%20that%20they%20can%20reach%20their%20end%20goal%20i.e.%20separate%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690393740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-03%2Fn-biren-singh_650x400_81489983463.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-interfere-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-after-mizoram-counterpart-zoramthanga-rally-4243479%22%2