%20eight%20hours%20and%20it%20is%20still%20raining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20level%20of%20Godavari%20is%20at%2047.3%20feet%20at%208%20pm%20today%2C%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20rise%20further.%20The%20river%20is%20flowing%20at%2048.1%20feet%20at%20Bhadrachalam%2C%20which%20is%20the%20second%20warning%20level)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2042%20tourists%20are%20said%20to%20have%20got%20stranded%20trapped%20in%20a%20deep%20forest%20area%20in%20Telangana's%20Mulugu%20district%20where%20they%20had%20gone%20to%20see%20the%20Muthyaladhara%2C%20the%20highest%20waterfalls%20in%20the%20state.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20their%20return%2C%20the%20hikers%20were%20reportedly%20unable%20to%20cross%20on%20foot%20as%20the%20water%20levels%20had%20risen%20and%20the%20flow%20was%20tough%20to%20negotiate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20teams%20including%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20police%20are%20trying%20to%20bring%20them%20to%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinister%20Satyavati%20Rathod%20has%20instructed%20officials%20to%20spare%20no%20effort%20at%20the%20earliest.%20The%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20is%20also%20being%20called%20in%20to%20help%20with%20in%20the%20rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20had%20declared%20holidays%20for%20all%20educational%20institutions%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690393740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fvjb4qh1c_telangana-woman-washed-away_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-camera-woman-in-group-trying-to-cross-river-slips-gets-carried-away-4243359%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incessant%20rain%20in%20Telangana%20has%20claimed%20one%20life.%20A%20woman%20was%20washed%20away%20while%20crossing%20the%20Kummaravagu%20river.%20She%20is%20still%20missing%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-camera-woman-in-group-trying-to-cross-river-slips-gets-carried-away-4243359%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-camera-woman-in-group-trying-to-cross-river-slips-gets-carried-away-4243359%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-camera-woman-in-group-trying-to-cross-river-slips-gets-carried-away-4243359%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sri%20Lanka%20President%20Says%20His%20Primary%20Aim%20Is%20To%20Discuss%2013th%20Amendment%20With%20All%20Parties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26231515%2FAll-party-leaders-meeting-03.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20asserted%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20July%2026%2C%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20discuss%20the%2013th%20Amendment%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20a%20key%20aspect%20of%20the%201987%20Indo-Lanka%20accord%20%E2%80%93%20with%20all%20parties%20as%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20that%20%E2%80%9Caffects%20the%20entire%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2013th%20Amendment%20called%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20provinces%20and%20decentralisation%20of%20powers%2C%20especially%20of%20police%20and%20land.%20While%20provinces%20have%20been%20created%20with%20their%20own%20administrations%2C%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20police%20and%20land%20continued%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Colombo.%20This%20has%20created%20resentment%20among%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamil%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWickremesinghe%20held%20an%20All-Party%20Conference%20at%20the%20Presidential%20Secretariat%20on%20Wednesday.%20He%20highlighted%20that%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20amendment%20should%20involve%20inputs%20from%20all%20relevant%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conference%20was%20organized%20to%20update%20the%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20party%20leaders%20on%20the%20National%20Reconciliation%20Program%20and%20the%20North-East%20Development%20Plan%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmd.gov.lk%2Fnews%2Fprimary-aim-is-to-discuss-the-13th-amendment-of-the-constitution-with-all-parties%2F%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20said%20that%20he%20does%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20pass%20new%20laws%20to%20address%20existing%20problems%20and%20that%20power%20rests%20solely%20with%20parliament.%20He%20was%20bringing%20forth%20%E2%80%9Crelevant%20proposals%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20country%2C%20but%20the%20%E2%80%9Cresponsibility%20of%20implementing%20them%20lay%20with%20all%20the%20representatives%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%20as%20he%20alone%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20achieve%20it%20with%20his%20single%20vote%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20the%20full%20implementation%20of%20the%2013th%20Amendment.%20However%2C%20Wickremesinghe%20is%20the%20sole%20MP%20of%20his%20party%20and%20his%20presidency%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20ruling%20Sri%20Lanka%20Podujana%20Peramuna%20(SLPP)%2C%20which%20has%20traditionally%20opposed%20the%20decentralisation%20of%20powers.%20There%20is%20not%20much%20hope%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20the%20current%20exercise%20would%20yield%20any%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Wickremesinghe%20suggested%20that%20the%20central%20government%20should%20formulate%20policies%20for%20the%20country%2C%20while%20provincial%20councils%20should%20provide%20the%20necessary%20facilities%20for%20the%20successful%20implementation%20of%20development%20activities%20in%20all%20fields.%20%E2%80%9CCollaboration%20between%20all%20parties%20and%20levels%20of%20government%20was%20crucial%20for%20progress%20and%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccollective%20discussions%E2%80%9D%20among%20all%20parties%20to%20decide%20on%20granting%20police%20powers%20to%20the%20provincial%20councils%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20President%20Wickremesinghe%20proposed%20arrangements%20that%20would%20allow%20members%20of%20the%20Provincial%20Councils%20to%20concurrently%20hold%20positions%20and%20be%20appointed%20as%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20while%20members%20of%20Parliament%20could%20also%20serve%20as%20members%20of%20the%20Provincial%20Councils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Wickremesinghe%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Dinesh%20Gunawardena%2C%20speaker%20Mahinda%20Yapa%20Abeywardena%2C%20opposition%20leader%20Sajith%20Premadasa%20and%20former%20president%20Maithripala%20Sirisena%20were%20among%20those%20who%20participated%20and%20expressed%20their%20views%20during%20the%20event.%20Numerous%20party%20leaders%20and%20representatives%20from%20various%20parties%20were%20also%20present%20at%20the%20occasion%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690393674000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26231515%2FAll-party-leaders-meeting-03.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lanka-president-says-his-primary-aim-is-to-discuss-13th-amendment-with-all-parties%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Amendment%2C%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%201987%20Indo-Lanka%20pact%2C%20called%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20provinces%20and%20decentralisation%20of%20powers%2C%20especially%20of%20police%20and%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lanka-president-says-his-primary-aim-is-to-discuss-13th-amendment-with-all-parties%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asked%20If%20He%20Was%20Faced%20With%20The%20Question%20Of%20Nepotism%2C%20Aditya%20Said...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBollywood%20actor%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur%20has%20been%20hogging%20all%20the%20limelight%20ever%20since%20his%20portrayal%20of%20Shaan%20Sengupta%20in%20the%20blockbuster%20web%20series%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Night%20Manager.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Now%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.filmfare.com%2Finterviews%2Fcover-story-aditya-roy-kapur-on-the-success-of-the-night-manager-pushing-himself-with-every-role-60057.html%5C%22%3EFilmfare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20actor%20has%20opened%20up%20about%20his%20initial%20days%20in%20the%20industry%20and%20on%20being%20faced%20with%20the%20question%20of%20nepotism.%20Talking%20to%20Filmfare%2C%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur%20said%20that%20he%20started%20in%20the%20industry%20by%20doing%20supporting%20roles%20hence%20nepotism%20didn't%20play%20a%20part%20in%20his%20journey%20as%20an%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20know%20that%20I%20have%20kind%20of%20made%20my%20way%20into%20the%20industry.%20I%20started%20with%20supporting%20roles%20in%20films%20my%20brothers%20weren't%20involved%20with.%20My%20journey%20has%20been%20a%20public%20one.%20People%20saw%20my%20career%20develop%20slowly.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20did%20my%20first%20leading%20role%2C%20I%20had%20already%20done%20three%20supporting%20parts.%20So%20I%20think%20that%20journey%20is%20clear%20for%20people%20to%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20his%20auditioning%20experiences%2C%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur%20emphasised%20that%20rejection%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20auditioning%20process%20however%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20the%20process%20in%20itself%20was%20never%20scarring%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20Filmfare%2C%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20be%20an%20actor%2C%20I%20think%20rejection%20is%20part%20of%20the%20process.%20You%20better%20get%20used%20to%20it.%20The%20early%20days%20of%20auditioning%20were%20pretty%20much%20a%20lot%20of%20no.%20I%20used%20to%20audition%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20stuff%20but%20it's%20not%20like%20I%20knew%20for%20sure%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20actor.%20I%20was%20an%20RJ%20and%20I%20was%20happy.%20%C2%A0I%20was%20never%20really%20into%20films.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20happened%20by%20chance.%20I%20used%20to%20go%20to%20certain%20auditions%20because%20people%20used%20to%20call%20me%20now%20and%20then.%20And%20I%20would%20audition%20because%20you%20never%20know%20what%20opportunities%20would%20come.%20But%20I%20don't%20think%20those%20early%20years%20scarred%20me%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20work%2C%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur%20is%20also%20trending%20big%20time%20with%20regard%20to%20his%20rumoured%20relationship%20with%20actress%20Ananya%20Panday.%20It%20so%20happened%20that%2C%20Ananya%20Panday%20watched%20Greta%20Gerwig's%20Barbie%20over%20the%20weekend%20and%20she%20was%20accompanied%20by%20the%20usual%20suspect%20-%20rumoured%20boyfriend%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Instagram%20user%20shared%20a%20video%20in%20which%20she%20can%20be%20seen%20clicking%20selfies%20with%20Ananya%20Panday%20and%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur%20from%20a%20movie%20hall%20that%20was%20screening%20the%20film.%20%26quot%3BMajor%20fan%20girl%20moment%20during%20the%20Barbie%20movie%20with%20Ananya%20Panday%20and%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fan%20captioned%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20the%20video%20posted%20by%20the%20fan%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvCf0ZdtHel%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvCf0ZdtHel%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_c