2024%2C%20some%201.4%20billion%20people%20from%20over%2060%20visa-exempt%20countries%20are%20required%20to%20have%20a%20travel%20authorisation%20to%20enter%20most%20European%20countries%2C''%20the%20EU%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftravel-europe.europa.eu%2Fetias%2Fwhat-etias_en%23etias-in-a-nutshell%5C%22%3Ewebsite%20noted.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20ETIAS%20is%20an%20electronic%20travel%20authorization%20linked%20to%20a%20traveler's%20passport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20U.S.%20citizens%20who%20want%20to%20travel%20to%20the%2027%20member%20countries%20of%20Europe's%20Schengen%20Zone%20will%20need%20to%20register%20with%20ETIAS%20or%20risk%20being%20turned%20away%20at%20the%20border.%C2%A0Once%20the%20authorization%20is%20secured%2C%20however%2C%20it%20is%20valid%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years%20or%20until%20the%20visitor's%20passport%20expires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ETIAS%2C%20most%20applications%20should%20be%20processed%20within%20minutes%2C%20but%20in%20case%20an%20application%20takes%20longer%2C%20decisions%20will%20be%20sent%20within%20four%20days%20or%20up%20to%2014%20days%20if%20the%20applicant%20is%20asked%20to%20provide%20additional%20documentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''With%20a%20valid%20ETIAS%20travel%20authorization%2C%20you%20can%20enter%20the%20territory%20of%20these%20European%20countries%20as%20often%20as%20you%20want%20for%20short-term%20stays%20%E2%80%94%20normally%20for%20up%20to%2090%20days%20in%20any%20180-day%20period.%20However%2C%20it%20does%20not%20guarantee%20entry.%20When%20you%20arrive%2C%20a%20border%20guard%20will%20ask%20to%20see%20your%20passport%20and%20other%20documents%20and%20verify%20that%20you%20meet%20the%20entry%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftravel-europe.europa.eu%2Fetias%2Fwho-should-apply_en%23ETIAS-countries%5C%22%3EEU's%20website%20reads.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Henley%20Passport%20Index%2C%20American%20trave