%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Thanks%20To%20PM%20Modi'%3A%20India%20Football%20Coach%20After%20Asian%20Games%20Clearance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20football%20fraternity%20of%20India%20was%20on%20cloud%20nine%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20the%20sports%20ministry%20gave%20a%20clearance%20to%20both%20men's%20and%20women's%20team%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Asian%20Games.%20The%20continental%20event%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Hangzhou%2C%20China%2C%20starting%20from%20September%2023.%20The%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20had%20earlier%20refused%20to%20clear%20the%20Indian%20football%20teams%20for%20the%20Asian%20Games%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20they%20were%20not%20ranked%20in%20the%20top-8%20in%20Asia.%20The%20All%20India%20Football%20Federation%20(AIFF)%20then%20made%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Sports%20Ministry%20to%20allow%20the%20men's%20and%20women's%20sides%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20prestigious%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20news%20of%20India%20getting%20the%20clearance%20came%20to%20light%2C%20national%20senior%20team%20head%20coach%20Igor%20Stimac%2C%20who%20had%20earlier%20asked%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20intervention%2C%20expressed%20his%20gratitude%20towards%20the%20authorities%20and%20stated%20that%20he%20will%20be%20using%20the%20upcoming%20King's%20Cup%20in%20Thailand%20to%20prepare%20the%20players%20for%20the%20Asian%20Games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20not%20forget%20to%20give%20special%20and%20big%20thanks%20to%20sports%20minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20to%20our%20general%20secretary%20Shaji%20Prabhakaran%20and%20especially%20to%20our%20president%2C%20Kalyan%20Chaubey%20for%20great%20efforts%20they%20put%20so%20that%20we%20can%20celebrate%20today.%20I%20am%20especially%20glad%20because%20so%20many%20of%20our%20supporters%20who%20were%20behind%2C%20sending%20message%2C%20emails%2C%20supporting%20the%20football%20culture%20in%20the%20country.%20So%2C%20it's%20a%20really%20important%20moment%20for%20us%20and%20hopefully%20a%20great%20chance%20for%20our%20youngsters%20to%20prove%20themselves%20on%20a%20big%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmualMmXlAAw%5C%22%3Esaid%20Stimac%20on%20Revsportz.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20great%20trust%20and%20faith%20in%20our%20youngsters%20and%20we%20will%20see%20what%20happens.%20It's%20still%20far%20away%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20September%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20work%20really%20hard%20on%20the%20preparation%20camp%20for%20such%20a%20tournament.%20First%20thing%20I%20have%20in%20mind%20is%20that%20I%20might%20use%20King's%20Cup%20in%20Thailand%20to%20prepare%20these%20boys%2C%20which%20is%20the%20only%20possible%20situation.%20Maybe%20give%20them%20opportunity%20to%20play%20against%20Iraq%2C%20Thailand%2C%20and%20whoever%20else%20is%20there%20to%20prepare%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20team%20under%20Croatian%20coach%20Igor%20Stimac%20has%20entered%20sub-100%20club%20in%20FIFA%20ranking%20once%20again%20having%20won%20SAFF%20championship%20where%20it%20played%20against%20Lebanon%20and%20Kuwait.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Stimac%2C%C2%A0AIFF%20President%20Kalyan%20Chaubey%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20indeed%20an%20important%20day%20for%20Indian%20Football%20and%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20resolution%20to%20develop%20the%20sport%20in%20India.%20We%20thank%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Sports%20%26amp%3B%20Youth%20Affairs%20for%20their%20support%20and%20for%20providing%20special%20compensation%20to%20Indian%20Football%20for%20the%2019th%20Asian%20Games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20Football%20has%20been%20on%20an%20unprecedented%20rise%20recently%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20this%20impetus%20will%20further%20boost%20our%20players'%20morale%20in%20all%20upcoming%20events.%20It's%20my%20honour%20to%20represent%20the%20All%20India%20Football%20Federation%20and%20with%20moments%20like%20this%2C%20it%20further%20encourages%20our%20steadfast%20commitment%20to%20continue%20developing%20the%20ecosystem%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Football%20Federation%20(AIFF)%20is%20bullish%20on%20sending%20its%20first%20team%20to%20the%20Asian%20Games%2C%20led%20by%20its%20talismanic%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Chhetri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F106840-sunil-chhetri-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Chhetri%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20team%20under%20Croatian%20coach%20Igor%20Stimac%20has%20entered%20sub-100%20club%20in%20FIFA%20ranking%20once%20again%20having%20won%20SAFF%20championship%20where%20it%20played%20against%20Lebanon%20and%20Kuwait.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690390740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fuaj0shn8_igor-stimac_650x300_09_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fspecial-thanks-to-pm-narendra-modi-india-football-coach-igor-stimac-after-teams-clearance-for-asian-games-4243217%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20football%20fraternity%20of%20India%20was%20on%20cloud%20nine%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20the%20sports%20ministry%20gave%20a%20clearance%20to%20both%20men's%20and%20women's%20team%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Asian%20Games.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fspecial-thanks-to-pm-narendra-modi-india-football-coach-igor-stimac-after-teams-clearance-for-asian-games-4243217%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fspecial-thanks-to-pm-narendra-modi-india-football-c