g%20to%20call%20the%20police%2C%20he%20ran%20away%2C%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20conducted%20a%20house-to-house%20search%20in%20the%20area%20and%20arrested%20him%20from%20one%20of%20the%20buildings.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20Hindu%20Rao%20Hospital%20for%20a%20medical%20examination%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(north)%20Sagar%20Singh%20Kalsi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20planning%20to%20sell%20the%20house%20of%20Shora%20Kothi%20as%20there%20was%20some%20water-related%20issue%20and%20also%20because%20he%20needed%20money%20for%20purchasing%20liquor.%20However%2C%20his%20mother%20refused%2C%20which%20made%20him%20angry%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20night%2C%20Indu%20informed%20Charu%20that%20Deepak%20had%20beaten%20her%20badly%20and%20feared%20that%20he%20might%20kill%20her.%20He%20further%20disclosed%20that%20both%20of%20them%20were%20in%20the%20same%20bedroom%20and%20his%20mother%20asked%20him%20to%20switch%20off%20the%20air%20conditioner%2C%20but%20he%20wanted%20to%20keep%20it%20on%2C%20DCP%20Kalsi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfuriated%20by%20the%20conversation%20between%20his%20mother%20and%20sister%2C%20he%20started%20beating%20Indu%20with%20a%20sharp-edged%20stick%2C%20causing%20multiple%20injuries%20on%20her%20head%2C%20face%2C%20neck%20and%20hand%20due%20to%20which%20she%20became%20unconscious%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20dragged%20her%20to%20another%20room%20and%20left%20her%20on%20the%20floor.%20He%20knew%20that%20Charu%20who%20lives%20in%20Nangloi%20would%20not%20come%20to%20his%20home%20at%20night%20and%20went%20to%20sleep%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20in%20another%20room%20leaving%20his%20unconscious%20mother%20alone%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690389840000%2C%22vis