g%20Societies%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20Konrad%20Adenauer%20Stiftung%20(KAS)%20in%2018%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%209%2C316%20%C2%A0respondents%20aged%20between%2015%20and%2034%20years%20were%20part%20of%20the%20survey%20carried%20out%20last%20year%20in%20November%20and%20December.%20The%20study%20aimed%20to%20understand%20different%20aspects%20of%20the%20country%20against%20different%20backdrops%20of%20five%20broad%20areas%20including%20employment%2C%20education%2C%20social%20ties%2C%20lifestyle%20preferences%2C%20and%20physical%20and%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%2213v22pcg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F13v22pcg_study_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20this%20study%20was%20undertaken%20after%20the%20devastating%20pandemic%2C%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20pandemic%20constitute%20an%20important%20backdrop%20to%20the%20views%20and%20lifestyles%20of%20today's%20youth%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20India's%20youth's%20preference%20for%20the%20field%20of%20study%2C%20the%20findings%20suggest%20that%20arts%20and%20humanities%20constitute%20the%20most%20studied%20area.%20More%20than%20one-third%20or%2035%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20respondents%20opted%20for%20humanities%2C%20followed%20by%20science%20(20%20per%20cent)%2C%20commerce%20management%20(8%20per%20cent)%20and%20engineering%20(5%20per%20cent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22f83l9jh%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ff83l9jh_survey_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20study%20delved%20into%20the%20employment%20profile%20of%20Indian%20youth%2C%20it%20found%20that%20presently%20about%20one-fourth%20or%2023%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20respondents%20were%20self-employed.%20It%20was%20followed%20by%2016%20per%20cent%20of%20youth%2C%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20professions%20like%20doctors%20and%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22949i4rkg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F949i4rkg_study_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarming%20was%20third%20with%2015%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20choosing%20it.%20Although%20a%20significant%20proportion%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20semi-unskilled%20(14%20per%20cent)%20work%20and%20skilled%20work%20(13%20per%20cent)%2C%20only%206%20per%20cent%20were%20in%20government%20jobs%20-%20a%20highly%20preferred%20sector%20for%20young%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22euhlfo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Feuhlfo_survey_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20backdrop%20of%20career%20aspirations%2C%20the%20findings%20suggested%20that%20the%20health%20sector%20was%20the%20most%20popular%20among%20the%20youth%20with%2016%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20desiring%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20it.%20While%20teaching%20jobs%20and%20business%20were%20at%20the%20second%20and%20fourth%20position%2C%20respectively%2C%20government%20jobs%20occupied%20sixth%20place%20in%20this%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20revealed%20that%20the%20country's%20youth%20identified%20unemployment%20as%20the%20biggest%20concern%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690389420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ft4v42c9g_youth-generic_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcsds-survey-reveals-majority-of-youth-prefers-government-job-over-private-and-business-4241871%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20survey-based%20study%20on%20Indian%20youth%20has%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20preferences%20of%20young%20citizens%20in%20terms%20of%20education%20streams%2C%20employment%20type%2C%20and%20career%20aspirations%20after%20the%20COVID-19%20p