span%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20animals%20are%20among%20the%20several%20that%20were%20released%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20the%20park%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%20%E2%80%93%20India%E2%80%99s%20intercontinental%20cheetah%20translocation%20programme%20%E2%80%93%20and%20are%20being%20brought%20back%20for%20health%20checks%20following%20fears%20of%20infections%20caused%20by%20radio%20collars.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPrabhas%20and%20Veera%20are%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMale%20cheetah%20Prabhas%20and%20female%20Veera%20were%20captured%20from%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno%20and%20brought%20back%20to%20enclosures%20in%20the%20park%20on%20July%2025%2C%20the%20forest%20department%20announced%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fminforestmp%2Fstatus%2F1683902932763254784%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Etweet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20animals%20are%20healthy%2C%20according%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20principal%20chief%20conservator%20of%20forest%20(wildlife)%20Aseem%20Srivastava.%20The%20animals%20will%20be%20kept%20in%20the%20enclosures%20until%20their%20next%20health%20check%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20leaves%20two%20cheetahs%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno%2C%20which%20have%20not%20undergone%20health%20checks%20yet%3A%20Nirva%20and%20Dhatri.%20On%20July%2024%2C%20a%20source%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fafter-blaming-deaths-on-natural-causes-authorities-carry-out-health-checks-of-cheetahs%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20catching%20these%20free-ranging%20individuals%20was%20proving%20%E2%80%98difficult%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwenty%20African%20cheetahs%20arrived%20in%20Kuno%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%20in%20September%20last%20year%20and%20March%20this%20year%2C%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah.%20Of%20these%2C%20five%20have%20died%20so%20far.%20Three%20cubs%20born%20in%20India%20have%20also%20died.%20The%20last%20two%20deaths%20%E2%80%93%20of%20adult%20males%20Tejas%20and%20Surya%20on%20July%2011%20and%2014%20%E2%80%93%20have%20courted%20controversy%20after%20experts%20said%20that%20moisture%20accumulation%20due%20to%20their%20radio%20collars%20caused%20wounds%20underneath%20the%20collars%20to%20be%20infected%20and%20that%20this%20brought%20on%20traumatic%20shock%2C%20and%20then%20death.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690388155000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20162049%2FFpPKPzyaUAIUrGc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftwo-more-cheetahs-brought-back-to-enclosures-in-kuno%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20forest%20department%2C%20the%20cheetahs%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0Prabhas%20and%20Veera%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0are%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99.%20Only%20two%20cheetahs%20now%20remain%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftwo-more-cheetahs-brought-back-to-enclosures-in-kuno%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20tweet%20boosts%20vaccine%20conspiracies%20targeting%20LeBron%20James'%20son%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690387752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F061A%2Fproduction%2F_130526510_bronnyjamesgettyimages-1488059047.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fhealth-66313916%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20basketball%20legend's%20son%20Bronny%20James%20suffered%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A738%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fhealth-66313916%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22http