ying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnothing%20will%20go%20on%20record%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20DMK%20MP%20Tiruchi%20Siva%20also%20pointed%20out%20to%20Dhankhar%20that%20Kharge%20was%20repeatedly%20interrupted%20while%20he%20was%20speaking%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20other%20members%20and%20was%20not%20able%20to%20convey%20what%20he%20wanted%20to%20say.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20unprecedented%20manner%2C%20when%20the%20floor%20was%20given%20to%20him%20and%20he%20was%20speaking%2C%20his%20mike%20was%20switched%20off.%20This%20has%20never%20happened%20in%20the%20past%20that%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20mike%20has%20been%20switched%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siva%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDhankhar%20then%20responded%20that%20he%20had%20received%20inputs%20from%20the%20deputy%20chairman%20and%20stated%20that%20no%20microphones%20were%20switched%20off.%20He%20added%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20that%20mikes%20were%20put%20off.%20If%20an%20honourable%20member%20transgresses%20to%20another%20issue%20that%20is%20not%20the%20subject%20of%20discussion%E2%80%A6%20That%20cannot%20be%20allowed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20also%20said%20that%20while%20media%20reports%20said%20that%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20had%20been%20suspended%20for%20raising%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20it%20was%20not%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSuspension%20was%20not%20because%20he%20raised%20an%20issue.%20He%20was%20suspended%20for%20misconduct%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eputting%20it%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20that%20a%20member%20was%20suspended%20because%20of%20raising%20an%20issue%20is%20unpardonable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%