%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20asserted%20in%20the%20state%20legislature%20today%20that%20police%20personnel%20will%20not%20be%20appointed%20on%20a%20contractual%20basis%20and%20said%20Mumbai%20faces%20a%20shortage%20of%20around%2010%2C000%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20made%20in%20the%20legislative%20council%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20said%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20has%20sought%203%2C000%20personnel%20from%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Security%20Corporation%20(MSSC)%2C%20an%20undertaking%20of%20the%20state%20police%2C%20to%20tide%20over%20the%20paucity%20of%20manpower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20is%20a%20shortage%20of%20around%2010%2C000%20personnel%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20police%20force%20and%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital%20cannot%20be%20safeguarded%20adequately%20with%20this%20shortfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNowhere%20are%20police%20personnel%20taken%20on%20contract%20and%20it%20will%20not%20be%20done%20(in%20Maharashtra)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20said%20in%20the%20Assembly%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20the%20statement%20in%20the%20council%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%20the%203%2C000%20personnel%20sought%20from%20MSSC%20will%20be%20used%20for%20providing%20security%2C%20guard-related%20duties%20and%20other%20static%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(MSSC%20personnel)%20will%20not%20be%20given%20any%20work%20related%20to%20investigation%20or%20implementation%20of%20law%20and%20order.%20There%20is%20no%20contractual%20hiring%20of%20police....%20no%20such%20proposal%20is%20under%20consideration%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0the%20home%20minister%20said%20in%20the%20Upper%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis'%20response%20came%20after%20criticism%20from%20the%20opposition%20which%20alleged%20police%20personnel%20were%20recruited%20on%20a%20contractual%20basis%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Mumbai%20police%20force%20has%2010%2C000%20vacant%20posts%20and%201%2C500%20personnel%20retire%20from%20service%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20fresh%20recruitment%20in%20the%20police%20force%20in%202019%2C%202020%20and%202021%2C%20and%20around%20500%20cops%20have%20succumbed%20to%20Covid-19%20since%20the%20pandemic%20broke%20out%20more%20than%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20process%20of%20state-wide%20recruitment%20of%2018%2C331%20police%20personnel%20has%20started.%20These%20include%2014%2C956%20police%20constables%2C%202%2C174%20drivers%20(of%20constable%20rank)%20and%20State%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(SRPF)%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2018%2C331%20police%20personnel%20being%20recruited%2C%207%2C076%20posts%20are%20of%20constables%20and%20994%20of%20drivers%20(of%20constable%20rank)%20for%20Mumbai%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20raising%20the%20issue%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20Congress%20MLA%20Nana%20Patole%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20(the%20government)%20are%20recruiting%20police%20personnel%20on%20a%20contract%20basis.%20Your%20ministers%20are%20also%20on%20contract.%20When%20they%20take%20a%20briefing%20(from%20officials)%2C%20they%20twist%20answers%20which%20is%20why%20questions%20take%20time%20to%20be%20answered.%20Give%20pointed%20replies.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20this%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%20no%20minister%20is%20on%20contract.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20(Mr%20Patole)%20want%20to%20come%20on%20contract%20then%20we%20will%20think%20about%20it.%20Nowhere%20are%20police%20personnel%20taken%20on%20contract%20and%20it%20will%20not%20be%20done%20(in%20the%20state)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20clarified.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20st