ce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2060%20years%2C%20India%20managed%20to%20electrify%20only%2020%2C%20000%20km%20of%20rail%20lines%20compared%20to%20the%2040%2C000%20km%20achieved%20by%20his%20government%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years...%20Now%20every%20month%2C%20we%20are%20completing%206%20km%20metro%20line%2C%20less%20than%204%20lakh%20km%20of%20village%20roads...%20In%202014%2C%20Delhi%20airport's%20capacity%20was%20around%205%20crore%20a%20year.%20Now%20it%20is%207.5%20crore...%20The%20number%20of%20airports%20has%20reached%20150%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20opposition%20too.%20Clubbing%20together%20his%20political%20rivals%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20while%20centres%20like%20the%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20enhances%20a%20country's%20profile%2C%20there%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bnegative%20minded%26quot%3B%20people%20who%20attempted%20to%20stop%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20people%20tried%20to%20stop%20this%20Bharat%20Mandapam.%20It%20is%20some%20people's%20compulsion%20to%20stop%20every%20work.%20In%20breaking%20news%2C%20what%20all%20was%20showed%3F%20So%20many%20cases%20were%20filed...%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20after%20a%20while%2C%20those%20people%20will%20come%20here%20for%20some%20lectures%20or%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690382700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fbr14a2p8_pm-modi-at-bharat-mandapam-pti-650_650x400_26_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsymbolic-of-indias-will-power-pm-modi-unveils-bharat-mandapam-4242520%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20assured%20that%20India%20will%20be%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20top%20three%20economies%20during%20his%20third%20term.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsymbolic-of-indias-will-power-pm-modi-unveils-