eers%20from%20around%20the%20world.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325110%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20has%20125%20students%20studying%20at%20minimal%20fees%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Lori%20Chauhan%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stayed%20in%20Sainji%20during%20the%20research%2C%20where%20she%20met%20her%20husband%20Kunwar%20Chauhan%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Epradhan%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20village%20and%20introduced%20himself.%20He%20was%20educated%20in%20Delhi%20but%20chose%20to%20return%20to%20his%20village%20as%20he%20wanted%20to%20work%20towards%20uplifting%20the%20area.%20We%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20in%20common%20besides%20our%20care%20for%20the%20village%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESparks%20flew%20and%20the%20two%20got%20married%20in%202007%2C%20and%20the%20couple%20settled%20in%20Sainji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%20a%20year%20into%20our%20marriage%2C%20many%20villagers%20would%20come%20and%20ask%20me%20if%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F264558%2Fengineer-teaches-ipl-cricket-commentary-free-english-language-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20could%20teach%20English%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20children.%20Soon%2C%20they%20started%20requesting%20if%20we%20could%20start%20an%20English%20medium%20school%20for%20the%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20for%20such%20requests%20was%20mostly%20because%20at%20that%20time%20there%20were%20no%20English%20medium%20schools%20nearby%2C%20and%20the%20ones%20in%20Mussoorie%20were%20not%20affordable%20for%20the%20villagers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20Garhwal%20English%20Medium%20School%2C%20which%20has%20over%20125%20students%20today%2C%20in%20classes%20starting%20from%20nursery%20to%20Class%208.%20Volunteers%20from%20England%2C%20Canada%20and%20other%20countries%20visit%20the%20school%20often%20as%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEight%20students%2C%20a%20cow%20shed%20and%20teacher%20Aunty%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20off%20really%20small%20with%20just%20eight%20students%20in%20a%20makeshift%20classroom%2C%20which%20was%20originally%20a%20cow%20shed.%20But%20this%20arrangement%20did%20not%20last%20long%20as%20we%20started%20to%20get%20more%20and%20more%20students%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20why%20I%20think%20we%20had%20such%20a%20big%20turnout%20was%20because%20the%20people%20here%20want%20to%20break%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty.%20Their%20children%20who%20go%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98044%2Fproject-kaleidoscope-taranagar-rajasthan-digital-education-piramal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20not%20able%20to%20face%20competition%20from%20children%20from%20private%20schools.%20They%20do%20not%20get%20admission%20to%20good%20colleges%20and%20many%20end%20up%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20villages%20to%20work%20on%20farms.%20The%20parents%20here%20really%20want%20their%20kids%20to%20come%20out%20of%20this%20