.com%2F323084%2Fmumbai-mother-son-duo-start-aazol-maharastrian-traditional-snacks-help-rural-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20mothers%3C%2Fa%3E%20Dr%20Saakshi%20Gulati%20(38)%20and%20Dr%20Nikita%20Mathur%20(34)%2C%20are%20making%20it%20come%20true.%20Dentists%20by%20profession%2C%20both%20are%20avid%20travellers.%20When%20they%20became%20mothers%20four%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%2C%20people%20told%20them%3A%20%E2%80%98You%20can%E2%80%99t%20travel%20once%20you%20have%20a%20child%E2%80%99.%20But%20they%20were%20determined%20to%20change%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaakshi%E2%80%99s%20first%20trip%20post-motherhood%20was%20to%20Mahabalipuram%20with%20her%20then%20three-month-old%20daughter.%20They%20enjoyed%20it%20so%20much%20that%20the%20couple%20took%20their%20daughter%20to%20Nainital%20and%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%20when%20she%20turned%20five%20months%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhereas%2C%20Nikita%2C%20who%20stays%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20took%20her%20older%20son%20to%20Mysuru%20when%20he%20was%20three%20months%20old.%20Her%20younger%20son%2C%20who%20is%20five%20months%20old%2C%20has%20already%20been%20to%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20travel%20blogging%20for%20eight%20years.%20After%20I%20had%20a%20child%2C%20people%20told%20me%20that%20it%20would%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20travel.%20Some%20even%20said%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20travel%20with%20a%20baby.%20I%20knew%20that%20it%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20true.%20After%20the%20initial%20three%20months%2C%20which%20were%20tough%2C%20we%20started%20travelling%20slowly.%20We%20had%20such%20a%20blast%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chennai-based%20Saakshi%2C%20who%20is%20a%20teacher%20at%20a%20dental%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThat%20cherished%20female%20friendship%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-gallery%20wp-block-gallery-1%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20si