r%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findia-is-open-to-doing-business-with-chinese-companies-says-rajeev-chandrasekhar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kukis%20in%20Manipur%20Are%20Fearful%20Like%20the%20Hindus%20of%20Noakhali%20Were%2C%20But%20Today%20India%20Has%20No%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26173324%2FNoakhali-gandhi-Manipur-Riots.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20bout%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20erupted%20on%20May%203.%20Since%20then%2C%20reports%20of%20looting%20and%20arson%20have%20been%20coming%20in%20continuously.%20But%20that%20large-scale%2C%20brutal%20sexual%20violence%20has%20also%20been%20carried%20out%20only%20came%20to%20light%20after%20a%20video%20went%20viral%20on%20July%2019.%20It%20finally%20forced%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20break%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20riots%20that%20have%20been%20going%20on%20for%20nearly%20three%20months.%20The%20chief%20minister%20also%20spoke%20up%20and%20promised%20action%20against%20the%20culprits.%20The%20incident%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20how%20violence%20in%20Noakhali%20was%20acknowledged%20by%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Bengal%2C%20Huseyn%20Shaheed%20Suhrawardy%2C%20only%20after%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20camped%20there%20and%20toured%20the%20district%20in%20a%20mission%20to%20restore%20communal%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201946%20Noakhali%20riot%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20most%20brutal%20episode%20of%20violence%20in%20pre-partition%20India.%20It%20was%20organised%20against%20the%20minority%20Hindus%20by%20the%20majority%20Muslim%20community%20in%20a%20planned%20manner%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20incumbent%20All%20India%20Muslim%20League%20government%20of%20the%20region.%20Following%20the%20call%20for%20Direct%20Action%20Day%20by%20Mohammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20demanding%20a%20separate%20Pakistan%2C%20a%20spate%20of%20violence%2C%20pogroms%2C%20looting%20and%20killing%20of%20Hindus%20in%20Calcutta%20erupted%20which%20continued%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20violence%20had%20government%20patronage%2C%20the%20victims%20received%20no%20help.%20Congress%20workers%20also%20felt%20helpless.%20Getting%20no%20support%20from%20outside%2C%20the%20Hindus%20decided%20to%20organise%20themselves%20into%20groups%20and%20took%20up%20arms%20against%20the%20Muslims.%20The%20League%20could%20not%20tolerate%20it%20and%20hence%20the%20Noakhali%20riots%20were%20planned%20in%20revenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoakhali%20was%20a%20Muslim-majority%20district%20in%20the%20Chittagong%20division.%20Here%2C%20the%20Hindu%20minority%20were%20mostly%20%3Cem%3Ezamindars%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20possessed%20vast%20tracts%20of%20land.%20The%20riots%20continued%20for%20several%20days.%20Reports%20of%20violence%20and%20killings%20were%20continuously%20reaching%20Delhi%20but%20no%20one%20could%20tell%20the%20actual%20magnitude%20of%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20Gandhi%20anxious%20despite%20the%20Bengal%20government%20denying%20all%20reports%20of%20violence%20and%20claiming%20that%20things%20were%20normal.%20Even%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20Calcutta%20had%20no%20clue%20of%20the%20real%20situation.%20Finally%2C%20one%20day%20Bapu%20asked%20the%20Congress%20president%20in%20his%20evening%20prayer%20meeting%20to%20visit%20the%20district%2C%20even%20if%20he%20faced%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20life.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20J.B.%20Kripalani%20left%20for%20Calcutta%20accompanied%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20Sucheta%20Kripalani%2C%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20reached%20Calcutta%2C%20the%20state%20Congress%20president%20told%20them%20that%20the%20rioters%20had%20blocked%20all%20routes%20to%20Noakhali%20and%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20visit%20it.%20He%20refused%20to%20accompany%20Kripalani%20out%20of%20fear.%20When%20Kripalani%20met%20Suhrawardy%2C%20the%20latter%20maintained%20his%20stance%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20fine%20and%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20go%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20discouraged%20so%2C%20the%20Kripalanis%20managed%20to%20reach%20the%20district%20only%20to%20find%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Hindus%20had%20been%20killed%20there.%20Dead%20bodies%20had%20piled%20up%20everywhere.%20Hindus%20had%20been%20forcefully%20evicted%20and%20their%20homes%20were%20captured.%20Forced%20religious%20conversions%20had%20been%20carried%20out.%20In%20addition%20to%20abduction%2C%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%2C%20girls%20were%20forced%20to%20convert%20and%20married%20off.%20Temples%20were%20pulled%20down.%20The%20ploughs%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ezamindars%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20set%20on%20fire%20and%20their%20oxen%20were%20slaughtered%20and%20cooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20Hindus%20who%20had%20managed%20to%20save%20themselves%20were%20so%20scared%20that%20they%20were%20hiding%20in%20clusters%20of%202-3%20families%20sharing%20a%20single%20room%20along%20with%20their%20animals.%20They%20remained%20hungry%20and%20thirsty%20for%20several%20days.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20single%20police%20or%20administrative%20official%20in%20the%20area.%20After%20taking%20stock%20of%20the%20situation%20for%20three%20days%2C%20J.B.%20Kripalani%20returned%20to%20Delhi.%20But%20Sucheta%20Kripalani%20stayed%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20when%20both%20of%20them%20decided%20to%20leave%2C%20a%20few%20Hindus%20requested%20JB%20to%20allow%20his%20wife%2C%20a%20motherly%20figure%20for%20the%20victims%2C%20to%20stay%20with%20them.%20Their%20pitiful%20exhortation%20left%20the%20couple%20speechless%20and%20Sucheta%20remained%20there%20for%20six%20months%20until%20Gandhi%20arrived%20there%20on%20November%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%20forced%20conversions%2C%20the%20events%20that%20unfolded%20in%20the%20violence%20against%20the%20Kuki%20community%20and%20women%20in%20Manipur%20bear%20stark%20similarity%20to%20the%20Noakhali%20riots.%20Sexual%20violence%20against%20women%20started%20as%20soon%20as%20ethnic%20violence%20erupted%20in%20the%20region%20on%20May%203.%20But%20neither%20the%20chief%20minister%20nor%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20nor%20the%20governor%20of%20Manipur%20who%20is%20a%20woman%2C%20nor%20the%20peace%20committee%20nor%20any%20army%20officer%2C%20even%20suggested%20that%20women%20were%20being%20subjected%20to%20violence%20there%20or%20made%20any%20effort%20to%20stop%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20this%20signify%3F%20Back%20then%20it%20was%20Suhrawardy%20who%20kept%20assuring%20everyone%20that%20everything%20was%20fine.%20And%20here%2C%20it%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98let%20things%20be%E2%80%99%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spate%20of%20violent%20attacks%20against%20women%20happened%20one%20after%20the%20other%20in%20May.%20Especially%20in%20Kuki-dominated%20area%20Churachandpur.%20Organised%20sexual%20violence%20and%20gang%20rape%20was%20perpetrated%20against%20them%20by%20members%20of%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community.%20According%20to%20the%20statements%20given%20by%20the%20Kuki%20rape%20victims%2C%20Meitei%20women%20were%20also%20inciting%20the%20mob%20to%20commit%20sexual%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20happened%20because%20on%20May%204%2C%20fake%20news%20was%20spread%20that%20Kuki%20men%20had%20raped%20a%20Meitei%20woman%20in%20Churachandpur.%20On%20May%205%2C%20the%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%20denied%20the%20news.%20The%20father%20of%20the%20girl%20who%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20raped%20also%20denied%20the%20reports.%20But%20by%20then%20the%20crowd%20had%20gone%20berserk.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20it%20was%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20police%20and%20the%20administration%20to%20pacify%20the%20people%20by%20taking%20them%20into%20confidence%2C%20but%20no%20such%20efforts%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Kuki%20women%20whose%20video%20has%20gone%20viral%20allege%20that%20the%20police%20themselves%20brought%20them%20out%20of%20the%20village%20and%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20the%20mob.%20The%20husband%20of%20one%20of%20these%20women%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20police%20station%20on%20May%2018%2C%20but%20no%20action%20was%20taken.%20The%20police%20(reluctantly)%20arrested%20the%20youth%20seen%20in%20the%20footage%20only%20when%20the%20video%20went%20viral%20after%20more%20than%2070%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20understand%20that%20there%20are%20mainly%20two%20communities%20in%20Manipur%20between%20whom%20there%20is%20an%20ongoing%20tussle.%20One%20is%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%2C%20who%20are%20tribals%2C%20Christian%20and%20dwell%20on%20the%20mountains.%20The%20Meiteis%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20are%20wealthier%20Hindus%20who%20have%20more%20participation%20in%20power%20and%20inhabit%20the%20plain%20areas.%20Now%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20are%20demanding%20that%20they%20be%20declared%20as%20tribal%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20that%20they%20too%20will%20get%20the%20right%20to%20buy%20tribal%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20big%20concern%20for%20Kuki%20and%20other%20tribal%20communities%20because%20it%20will%20make%20the%20Meiteis%20even%20stronger.%20The%20conflict%20of%20interest%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20is%20quite%20old.%20Needless%20to%20mention%2C%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20also%20a%20Meitei.%20If%20he%20wanted%2C%20he%20could%20have%20used%20his%20influence%20to%20pacify%20his%20community%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20women.%20But%20when%20it%20is%20about%20Hindu%20nationalism%2C%20then%20a%20free%20rein%20has%20to%20be%20given.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20is%20happening.%20Had%20the%20ill-fated%20video%20not%20come%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20would%20still%20be%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20he%20spoke%2C%20he%20dragged%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20that%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20brought%20shame%20to%20the%20country.%20Wrong.%20What%20has%20put%20us%20to%20shame%20is%20a%20prime%20minister%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20everyday%20rape%20incidents%20and%20deliberate%20sexual%20violence%20carried%20out%20as%20part%20of%20caste%20riots.%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20his%20statements%20are%20enough%20to%20enrage%20any%20sensitive%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20chose%20to%20remain%20silent%20and%20the%20governor%20depended%20on%20social%20media%20for%20information%2C%20how%20could%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20Rekha%20Sharma%2C%20question%20the%20Manipur%20police%20and%20the%20administration%3F%20Two%20women%20from%20Manipur%20and%20the%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Association%2C%20whose%20headquarters%20are%20abroad%2C%20had%20informed%20the%20Commission%20about%20such%20incidents%20through%20a%20letter%20mailed%20on%20June%2012.%20Believing%20the%20Commission%20to%20be%20the%20protector%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20honour%2C%20and%20constitutional%20and%20human%20rights%2C%20they%20requested%20it%20to%20take%20suo%20moto%20cognisance%20of%20the%20incidents%2C%20take%20action%20and%2C%20if%20possible%2C%20set%20up%20an%20inquiry%20committee.%20But%20they%20did%20not%20even%20receive%20an%20acknowledgment%20of%20the%20mail%20from%20the%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mail%20should%20have%20sufficed%20for%20Sharma%20to%20take%20action%20and%20send%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20representatives%20to%20the%20spot%20to%20get%20the%20matter%20investigated.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20video%20which%20evoked%20some%20sort%20of%20a%20response%20from%20her%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20hasty%20tweet.%20If%20a%20tweet%20had%20the%20power%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20would%20not%20have%20despatched%20a%20large%20number%20of%20central%20forces%20there.%20Clearly%2C%20Sharma%20missed%20the%20chance%20to%20win%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20trust%20and%20pacify%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwati%20Maliwal%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Commission%2C%20has%20announced%20that%20she%20will%20visit%20the%20state%2C%20but%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20she%20will%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20any%20work%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20Centre%2C%20considering%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20talk%20about%20the%20media.%20Most%20of%20the%20major%20newspapers%20and%20TV%20channels%20in%20Manipur%20belong%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20are%20not%20reporting%20much%20about%20the%20violence%20against%20the%20Kukis.%20The%20%3Cem%3ESangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20call%20the%20community%20%E2%80%98alien%E2%80%99.%20But%20the%20national%20media%20also%20received%20information%20about%20the%20organised%20sexual%20violence%20happening%20in%20the%20state%20only%20through%20the%20viral%20video.%20Why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20leave%20aside%20TV%20channels%20based%20in%20Delhi%20as%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deem%20it%20important%20enough%20to%20be%20discussed%20even%20after%20they%20had%20received%20information.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20have%20demonstrated%20that%20anarchy%20is%20acceptable%20to%20them.%20If%20it%20were%20not%20so%2C%20the%20love%20affair%20of%20Seema%20Haider%2C%20who%20eloped%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20would%20not%20have%20been%20the%20primetime%20story%20on%20every%20channel%20bar%20a%20few.%20Why%20did%20major%20English%20newspapers%2C%20with%20a%20network%20in%20the%20North-East%20as%20well%2C%20fail%20to%20find%20out%20about%20the%20violence%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20detailed%20report%20on%20sexual%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20was%20published%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20July%2012.%20Earlier%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20published%20an%20article%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20calls%20for%20the%20media%20to%20introspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20peace%20is%20really%20to%20be%20established%20in%20Manipur%2C%20then%20someone%20will%20have%20to%20camp%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20way%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20did%20in%20Noakhali.%20He%20went%20there%20with%20his%20entire%20team%2C%20stayed%20there%20for%20three%20months%20and%20surveyed%20the%20area%20barefoot.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20the%20entire%20land%20had%20become%20a%20crematorium%20for%20its%20people%20and%20walking%20on%20it%20with%20shoes%20on%20would%20be%20an%20insult%20to%20them.%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20bring%20himself%20to%20do%20so.%20He%20stayed%20at%20the%20houses%20of%20Muslim%20attackers%20and%20inspired%20them%20to%20help%20resettle%20the%20Hindus%20back%20in%20their%20houses.%20He%20got%20them%20to%20embrace%20each%20other%20by%20removing%20the%20mistrust%20and%20hatred%20between%20the%20two%20communities.%20Peace%20and%20relief%20committees%20were%20set%20up.%20He%20left%20the%20place%20only%20after%20things%20had%20calmed%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20of%20Noakhali%20and%20the%20restoration%20of%20peace%20in%20the%20region%20by%20Gandhi%20are%20both%20remarkable%20events%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%20We%20must%20learn%20from%20our%20past.%20The%20Kukis%20of%20Manipur%20are%20in%20a%20state%20of%20fear%20today%20similar%20to%20what%20the%20Hindu%20community%20must%20have%20felt%20in%20Noakhali%20back%20then.%20But%20does%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20have%20anyone%20who%20could%20be%20a%20Gandhi%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20bigger%20question%20is%20whether%20they%20really%20want%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20happening%20under%20the%20patronage%20of%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20government%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20only%20if%20the%20objective%20of%20the%20majoritarian%20violence%20has%20been%20achieved.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20different%20matter%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20intervenes%2C%20as%20the%20chief%20justice%20has%20said%20%E2%80%93%20or%20if%20the%20Kuki%20women%E2%80%99s%20heartfelt%20pleas%20inspire%20the%20president%20to%20issue%20some%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENeelam%20Gupta%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20former%20Adjunct%20Professor%20at%20Gujarat%20Vidyapith%2C%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F254059%2Fmanipur-violence-noakhali-riots-mahatma-gandhi-narendra-modi%2F%5C%22%3EHindi%20original%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690373518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26173324%2FNoakhali-gandhi-Manipur-Riots.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkukis-in-manipur-are-fearful-like-the-hindus-of-noakhali-were-but-today-india-has-no-gandhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20history%20of%20India%2C%20both%20the%20violence%20of%20Noakhali%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%20peace%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20by%20camping%20there%20are%20remarkable%20events.%20If%20peace%20is%20really%20to%20be%20established%20in%20Manipur%2C%20then%20a%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20will%20have%20to%20go%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkukis-in-manipur-are-fearful-like-the-hindus-of-noakhali-were-but-today-india-has-no-gandhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Believes%20In%20Rule%20by%20Chaos%20in%20Manipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20high%20time%20we%20started%20asking%20about%20the%20complicity%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20which%20has%20devastated%20Manipur.%20And%20hold%20the%20prime%20minister%20responsible%20for%20it.%20It%20needs%20to%20be%20said%20that%20by%20remaining%20proactively%20%E2%80%98inactive%E2%80%99%20in%20Manipur%2C%20it%20has%20succeeded%20in%20creating%20a%20long%20lasting%2C%20if%20not%20permanent%20division%20in%20the%20entire%20North%20Eastern%20region.%20It%20is%20no%20mean%20achievement%20for%20a%20party%20which%20rules%20by%20creating%20more%20and%20more%20division%20and%20chaos%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20inconceivable%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20has%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdilution-of-article-370-brought-unprecedented-progress-and-security-to-jk-centre-tells-sc%5C%22%3Eability%20to%20silence%20all%20voices%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20proactively%20intervenes%20through%20its%20agencies%20in%20West%20Bengal%20or%20other%20states%2C%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20despite%20saying%20it%20wants%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20commentariat%20and%20the%20opposition%20too%20has%20been%20treating%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20as%20an%20act%20of%20callous%20indifference%20on%20its%20part.%20The%20blame%20is%20being%20put%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-video-tarnished-states-image-says-cm-biren-calls-for-statewide-protests%5C%22%3EBiren%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rightly%20so.%20But%20how%20do%20we%20explain%20the%20failure%20of%20a%20Union%20government%20headed%20by%20a%20man%20who%20keeps%20asking%20the%20people%20across%20India%20to%20give%20power%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20states%20too%20so%20that%20he%20can%20directly%20control%20their%20affairs%20at%20the%20state-level%20too%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20say%20that%20it%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20contain%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20despite%20the%20presence%20of%20an%20unprecedented%20number%20of%20central%20security%20forces%20and%20the%20extraordinary%20power%20that%20it%20has%20assumed%20by%20sending%20its%20special%20representative%20to%20%E2%80%98help%E2%80%99%20the%20state%20government%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20it%20failure%2C%20or%20unwillingness%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20been%20said%20by%20veteran%20police%20officers%20and%20civil%20servants%20that%20if%20violence%2C%20especially%20communal%20violence%2C%20continues%20for%20more%20than%2024%20hours%2C%20it%20means%20the%20authorities%20do%20not%20want%20it%20to%20stop%20and%20are%20very%20much%20part%20of%20it.%20Imagine%20a%20whole%20state%20engulfed%20by%20sectarian%20violence%20for%20nearly%20three%20months!%20It%20was%20evident%20from%20day%20one%20that%20the%20state%20government%20was%20not%20too%20keen%20to%20stop%20the%20bloodshed.%20A%20government%20which%20justifies%20all%20its%20actions%20in%20the%20name%20of%20internal%20security%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20the%20control%20of%20the%20security%20of%20large%20areas%20of%20states%20which%20border%20other%20countries%2C%20allows%20a%20border%20state%20like%20Manipur%20to%20burn%20for%20three%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20must%20be%20a%20design%20behind%20this%20purported%20helplessness.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20we%20talk%20about%20it%2C%20we%20must%20also%20first%20describe%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20violence.%20Now%20all%20observers%20agree%20that%20Meitei%20majoritarian%20groups%20actively%20aided%20by%20the%20state%20police%2C%20have%20taken%20over%20the%20valley.%20There%20is%20no%20hiding%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20himself%20is%20the%20patron%20of%20these%20groups.%C2%A0%20Their%20leaders%20have%20openly%20expressed%20their%20intent%20to%20exterminate%20the%20Kuki%20population.%20No%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20them.%20Are%20we%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20let%20them%20roam%20free%20is%20Biren%20Singhs%20alone%3F%20That%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20its%20special%20representative%20sitting%20in%20Manipur%20cannot%20do%20anything%20to%20get%20the%20CM%20to%20reign%20these%20extremists%20in%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECould%20it%20be%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20like%20the%20state%20government%20in%20Imphal%2C%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20ending%20this%20majoritarian%20violence%3F%20That%20it%20wants%20this%20violence%20to%20run%20its%20course%20to%20achieve%20a%20definite%20purpose%3A%20of%20creating%20permanent%20division%20in%20Manipur%20so%20that%20it%20can%20better%20control%20the%20state%20and%20its%20resources%20by%20fragmenting%20it%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO-300x150.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO-1024x513.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO-800x400.jpeg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659017%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22601%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40NBirenSingh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20crisis%20drags%20on%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20Manipur%20violence%20casting%20its%20malevolent%20shadows%20beyond%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20borders.%20The%20attack%20on%20Kukis%20had%20already%20created%20disquiet%20in%20Mizoram.%20Now%20we%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmeiteis-begin-to-leave-mizoram-after-threat-manipur-govt-says-willing-to-provide-flights-8855091%2F%5C%22%3Ethreats%20being%20issued%20to%20Meiteis%20in%20Mizoram%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20first%20and%20immediate%20response%20of%20the%20Manipur%20CM%20is%20to%20announce%20special%20plane%20services%20to%20evacuate%20Meiteis.%20Neither%20the%20state%2C%20nor%20the%20Union%20government%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20halt%20the%20violence%20and%20insecurity.%20After%20that%2C%20Meitei%20groups%20have%20issued%20threats%20to%20the%20Mizos%20living%20in%20the%20Barak%20valley%20of%20Assam.%20The%20Nagas%2C%20who%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20they%20should%20be%20left%20alone%2C%20are%20restless.%20In%20Meghalaya%2C%20in%20the%20very%20initial%20days%20of%20violence%2C%20local%20groups%20had%20said%20that%20people%20displaced%20from%20Manipur%20should%20not%20be%20given%20hospitality%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20demand%20for%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20is%20being%20made%20by%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20it%20would%20definitely%20find%20an%20echo%20in%20other%20regions%20as%20all%20%E2%80%98natives%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98indigenous%E2%80%99%20people%20would%20want%20to%20secure%20their%20lands%20from%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20whole%20region%2C%20which%20was%20getting%20stable%20after%20decades%20of%20conflicts%2C%20has%20now%20been%20destabilised.%20It%20does%20not%20need%20great%20imagination%20to%20conclude%20that%20dormant%20militant%20factions%20will%20seek%20to%20regroup%20and%20rearm%20themselves%20with%20the%20support%20of%20their%20communities%C2%A0as%20they%20do%20not%20trust%20the%20state%20governments%20anymore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20ironic%20it%20is%20to%20see%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Social%20Powers%20Act(%20AFSPA)%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Manipuris%2C%20the%20very%20people%20who%20had%20been%20opposing%20it%20tooth%20and%20nail%20for%20the%20last%20several%20decades.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20dangerously%20naive%20to%20think%20that%20all%20this%20is%20happening%20without%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Any%20government%20which%20cares%20for%20the%20nation%20would%20do%20everything%20to%20restore%20peace%20and%20order%20in%20the%20country%20and%20society.%20But%20the%20record%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20one%20of%20creating%20chaos.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChaos%2C%20uncertainty%20and%20instability%20are%20very%20helpful%20for%20authoritarian%20governments%20because%20they%20create%20confusion%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20people.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20fail%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20world%20around%20them%20and%20are%20numbed%20into%20silence.%20We%20have%20seen%20the%20Modi%20government%20destabilising%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people%20through%20demonetisation%2C%20GST%20and%20the%20sudden%20lockdown.%20During%20the%20the%20second%20COVID-19%20wave%2C%20we%20saw%20it%20controlling%20the%20supply%20of%20oxygen%2C%20making%20people%20run%20around%20in%20desperation%20and%20then%20entering%20the%20scene%20when%20chaos%20had%20run%20its%20course.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20instability%20and%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20is%20also%20good%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20as%20it%20can%20go%20to%20voters%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CHindi%20Belt%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20threat%20and%20a%20promise.%20The%20threat%20is%20of%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%20taking%20over%20the%20North%20East%20region%20and%20the%20promise%20is%20of%20controlling%20them.%20The%20figure%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98outsider%E2%80%99%20is%20what%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20wants%20to%20keep%20alive%20to%20scare%20the%20electorate%20into%20voting%20for%20it%20for%20their%20security.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20PM%20but%20his%20refusal%20to%20end%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20which%20is%20proof%20of%20his%20complicity%20it%20it.%20One%20needs%20to%20note%20that%20in%20the%20first%20remarks%20on%20the%20crisis%20that%20he%20made%20in%2078%20days%2C%20he%20chose%20not%20to%20speak%20a%20word%20about%20Manipur%20itself%20but%20only%20about%20the%20incident%20related%20to%20the%20viral%20video.%20Taking%20a%20cue%20from%20him%2C%20top%20ministers%20and%20TV%20anchors%20have%20now%20made%20%E2%80%98violence%20against%20women%E2%80%99%20the%20issue%20and%20not%20the%20orchestrated%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20of%20which%20the%20horrific%20attack%20on%20women%20seen%20in%20that%20video%20is%20a%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20this%20leads%20us%20to%20only%20one%20conclusion%3A%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20not%20at%20all%20bothered%20by%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20Its%20silence%20and%20inaction%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20ongoing%20chaos%20is%20advantageous%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Who%20cares%20if%20India%20is%20cut%20to%20pieces%20and%20devoured%20by%20this%20majoritarian%20politics%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690371928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-believes-in-rule-by-chaos-in-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Could%20it%20be%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20like%20the%20state%20government%20in%20Imphal%2C%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20ending%20this%20majoritarian%20violence%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-believes-in-rule-by-chaos-in-manipur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Qatar%20sovereign%20fund%20in%20talks%20for%20%241%20billion%20stake%20in%20Reliance%20Retail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690371534000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-10%2F18%2Ffull%2F1634580965-3535.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fqatar-sovereign-fund-in-talks-for-1-billion-stake-in-reliance-retail-123072600565_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Qatar's%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20is%20in%20early%20discussions%20to%20buy%20a%20minority%20stake%20in%20billionaire%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20rapidly%20expanding%20retail%20unit%20for%20about%20%241%20billion%20(Rs%208%2C200%20crore)%2C%20sources%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fqatar-sovereign-fund-in-talks-for-1-billion-stake-in-reliance-retail-123072600565_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Behind%20the%20Scenes%20Look%20at%20Organising%20the%20First%20Ever%20IPL%20Tournament%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162447%2FWith-Virender-Sehwag-captain-Delhi-Daredevils-2008.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPutting%20things%20together%20was%20particularly%20challenging%20because%20nothing%20in%20Delhi%20is%20easy.%20It%20is%20a%20city%20with%20a%20flourishing%20VIP%20culture%20where%20everyone%20is%20a%20heavyweight%20ready%20to%20throw%20their%20weight%20around.%20Delhi%20is%20about%20power%20and%20entitlement%3B%20it%20is%20about%20government%20regulations%20and%20people%20who%20must%20be%20%E2%80%98obliged%E2%80%99.%20Holding%20a%20commercial%20cricket%20tournament%20in%20such%20an%20environment%20tested%20the%20notion%20of%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20working%20with%20the%20DDCA%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%20It%20had%20a%20well-earned%20reputation%20as%20a%20divided%20house%20constantly%20in%20a%20state%20of%20civil%20war%20and%20internal%20insurgency.%20The%20silver%20lining%20in%20the%20otherwise%20dark%20scenario%20was%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20the%20one-man%20DRS%20(dispute%20resolution%20system)%20who%2C%20whenever%20there%20was%20a%20disagreement%2C%20heard%20your%20appeal%20for%20relief%20and%20fair%20play%20and%20passed%20a%20nuanced%20judgement.%20Jaitley%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20was%20needed%20often%20because%20the%20IPL%20disturbed%20the%20power%20equation%20within%20state%20associations.%20During%20the%20IPL%2C%20control%20of%20stadium%20facilities%20shifted%20from%20association%20officials%20to%20team%20owners%2C%20a%20change%20resented%20by%20the%20local%20cricket%20dons%20because%20it%20meant%20the%20tenants%20were%20calling%20the%20shots%20instead%20of%20the%20landlords.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20395px)%2085vw%2C%20395px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162543%2FPitchside_Front.jpg_page-0001.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22395%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162543%2FPitchside_Front.jpg_page-0001.jpg%20794w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162543%2FPitchside_Front.jpg_page-0001-199x300.jpg%20199w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162543%2FPitchside_Front.jpg_page-0001-678x1024.jpg%20678w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665251%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22597%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAmrit%20Mathur%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EPitchside%3A%20My%20Life%20in%20Indian%20Cricket%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EWestland%20Sport%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20IPL%20demanded%20%E2%80%98world-class%E2%80%99%20standards%20and%20a%20good%20%E2%80%98fan%20experience%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20ground%20was%20another%20reason%20for%20franchise%20teams%20to%20sweat.%20The%20IPL%20small%20print%20included%20designer%20invites%2C%20a%20consistent%20%E2%80%98look%20and%20feel%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20fine%20dining%20with%20customised%20crockery%20and%20branded%20napkins.%20The%20league%20was%20positioned%20as%20the%20big%20fat%20Indian%20wedding%3A%20grand%20in%20scale%2C%20full%20of%20glitter%20and%20glamour%2C%20noisy%20and%20garish.%20The%20IPL%20matches%20were%20pitched%20as%20events%2C%20concept%20that%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20ordinary%20BCCI%20games%20where%20it%20was%20enough%20to%20mark%20the%20wicket%20and%20get%2022%20players%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kotla%20infrastructure%20was%20not%20even%20remotely%20world-class.%20The%20ground%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20floodlights%20or%20essential%20facilities%20for%20spectators.%20The%20Delhi%20Daredevils%20hired%20a%20cleaning%20agency%20a%20month%20before%20Kotla%E2%80%99s%20first%20IPL%20match%20in%202008%20to%20get%20the%20stadium%20spruced%20up%20in%20time.%20We%20discovered%2C%20not%20to%20our%20surprise%2C%20that%20there%20were%20parts%20of%20the%20ground%20that%20had%20not%20met%20a%20brush%20or%20a%20bottle%20of%20cleaning%20liquid%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecuring%20permissions%20to%20stage%20the%20event%20was%20also%20sheer%20torture.%20Several%20government%20agencies%20had%20to%20be%20satisfied%20(police%2C%20entertainment%20tax%2C%20electricity%20and%20water%2C%20fire%2C%20disaster%20management)%20and%20getting%20the%20paperwork%20done%20eventually%20boiled%20down%20to%20delicate%20negotiations%20over%20free%20tickets%20and%20passes.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20managing%20the%20distribution%20of%20freebies%20is%20a%20highly%20valued%20skill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20operations%20standpoint%2C%20besides%20the%20standard%20drill%2C%20one%20had%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20the%20anti-dew%20treatment%20before%20an%208%20a.m.%20game%20and%20fogging%20the%20playing%20area%20to%20keep%20mosquitos%20away.%20Generators%20had%20to%20be%20hired%20to%20guard%20against%20power%20failure%20and%20security%20guards%20were%20hired%20to%20guard%20the%20generators%20and%20prevent%20sabotage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20deployed%20almost%202%2C000%20personnel%20for%20overall%20security%2C%20background%20checks%20of%20people%20and%20sanitising%20the%20stadium.%20On%20match%20days%2C%20sniffer%20dogs%20checked%20the%20premises%20and%20scanners%2C%20metal%20detectors%20and%20CCTVs%20were%20installed%20at%20strategic%20points.%20Security%20was%20strict%20to%20the%20point%20where%20spectators%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20bring%20pens%20or%20coins%20into%20the%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20frantic%20efforts%20to%20tie%20up%20all%20the%20loose%20ends%20we%20came%20close%20to%20breaking%20point%20on%20many%20occasions.%20The%20accreditation%20system%20collapsed%20just%20before%20the%20first%20home%20game%2C%20leading%20to%20extreme%20panic%20because%2C%20without%20proper%20IDs%2C%20the%20police%20refused%20to%20allow%20players%2C%20umpires%20and%20the%20ground%20staff%20in.%20When%20the%20ticket%20box%20office%20opened%20at%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20Stadium%2C%20the%20rush%20was%20such%20that%20the%20police%20had%20to%20be%20called%20to%20restore%20order.%20Some%20scalpers%20were%20arrested%20for%20selling%20tickets%20in%20%E2%80%98black%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20development%20which%20led%20to%20an%20investigation%20to%20determine%20whether%20franchise%20insiders%20were%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20also%20the%20horror%20when%20we%20were%20left%20with%20unsold%20tickets%20for%20lower-end%20seats%20for%20some%20games.%20As%20empty%20stands%20look%20bad%20on%20television%2C%20schoolchildren%20were%20bussed%20into%20the%20stadium%20and%20given%20free%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chaos%20in%20the%20exclusive%20hospitality%20areas%20was%20even%20more%20troubling.%20The%20high-end%20corporate%20boxes%20were%20marketed%20as%20a%20khaana-peena-daaru%20deal%20that%20promised%20five-star%20catering%20and%20premium%20liquor.%20The%20strategy%20worked.%20However%2C%20an%20unexpected%20snag%20developed%20when%20hordes%20of%20gatecrashers%20invaded%20the%20hospitality%20boxes.%20Security%20broke%20down%2C%20drunken%20brawls%20took%20place%20and%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20public%20disorder%2C%20unruly%20behaviour%20and%20hooliganism.%20A%20concerned%20senior%20officer%20gave%20me%20friendly%20advice%3A%20Free%20daaru%20ko%20roko.%20Yeh%20Dilli%20culture%20mein%20nahi%20chalta.%20Arun%20Jaitley%20supported%20the%20liquor%20ban%20for%20a%20similar%20reason.%20During%20the%20matches%2C%20his%20box%20was%20full%20of%20uninvited%20guests%20who%20raided%20the%20food%20counter%20and%20polished%20off%20the%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162802%2FIPL-Match-Delhi.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162802%2FIPL-Match-Delhi.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162802%2FIPL-Match-Delhi-300x279.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162802%2FIPL-Match-Delhi-1024x951.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665253%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAt%20an%20IPL%20match%20in%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20control%20this%2C%20he%20switched%20to%20a%20strict%20no%20alcohol%2C%20only%20soft%20drinks%E2%80%99%20policy%20in%20his%20box.%20This%20worked%3A%20the%20number%20of%20Gate%20crashers%20dropped%20and%20order%20was%20restored.By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20IPL%20season%20four%20FIRs%20had%20been%20filed%20against.%20Me%2C%20the%20Daredevils%E2%80%99%20chief%20operating%20officer%2C%20for%20black%20marketing%20of%20tickets%2C%20overcharging%20for%20food%20items%20in%20the%20stadium%2C%20betting%20on%20games%2C%20and%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98indecent%20behaviour%E2%80%99%20of%20cheerleaders.%20Lesson%20learnt%20about%20the%20golden%20rule%20for%20successful%20match-day%20operations%3A%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20which%20big%20shot%20you%20have%20on%20speed%20dial%20in%20Delhi%2C%20just%20ensure%20that%20two%20key%20people%20are%20on%20your%20side%E2%80%94the%20local%20SHO%20and%20the%20entertainment%20tax%20officer.%20Without%20these%20two%20in%20your%20corner%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20organise%20matches%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20with%20permission%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3EPitchside%3A%20My%20Life%20in%20Indian%20Cricket%3Cem%3E%C2%A0by%20Amrit%20Mathur%2C%20published%20by%20Westland%20Sport%2C%20an%20imprint%20of%20Westland%20Books.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690370122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162447%2FWith-Virender-Sehwag-captain-Delhi-Daredevils-2008.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fa-behind-the-scenes-look-at-organising-the-first-ever-ipl-tournament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IPL%20matches%20were%20pitched%20as%20events%2C%20a%20concept%20that%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20ordinary%20BCCI%20games%20where%20it%20was%20enough%20to%20mark%20the%20wicket%20and%20get%2022%20players%20on%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fa-behind-the-scenes-look-at-organising-the-first-ever-ipl-tournament%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Axis%20Bank%20Q1FY24%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20up%2040.5%25%20YoY%2C%20gross%20NPAs%20down%20to%201.96%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690369686000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-04%2F27%2Ffull%2F1619523019-4025.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Faxis-bank-q1fy24-results-net-profit-up-40-5-yoy-gross-npas-down-to-1-96-123072600608_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Axis%20Bank's%20balance%20sheet%20grew%2013%25%20YOY%20and%20stood%20at%20Rs%201.3%20trillion%20as%20on%20June%2030%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Faxis-bank-q1fy24-results-net-profit-up-40-5-yoy-gross-npas-down-to-1-96-123072600608_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Faxis-bank-q1fy24-results-net-profit-up-40-5-yoy-gross-npas-down-to-1-96-123072600608_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Faxis-bank-q1fy24-results-net-profit-up-40-5-yoy-gross-npas-down-to-1-96-123072600608_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Has%20Classic%20Psychology%20Warped%20Our%20View%20of%20Human%20Nature%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26143853%2F06f6c811db2dec276447b8c92f50-1452799.jpgd_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20classic%20experiments%20and%20theories%20that%20every%20psychology%20student%20learns%20about%2C%20but%20more%20recent%20research%20has%20questioned%20their%20findings%20so%20that%20psychologists%20today%20are%20reevaluating%20human%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20Philip%20Zimbardo%E2%80%99s%201971%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fexhibits.stanford.edu%2Fspe%5C%22%3EStanford%20prison%20experiment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%2024%20participants%20were%20randomly%20separated%20into%20groups%20of%20would-be%20prisoners%20and%20guards.%20Within%20days%2C%20the%20research%20recorded%20that%20the%20guards%20were%20mistreating%20the%20prisoners%2C%20who%20began%20to%20display%20signs%20of%20distress.%20The%20abuse%20and%20distress%20became%20seemed%20so%20acute%20the%20experiment%20had%20to%20be%20curtailed%20after%20six%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20classic%20psychological%20theory%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newscientist.com%2Farticle%2F2207693-bystander-effect-famous-psychology-result-could-be-completely-wrong%2F%5C%22%3Ebystander%20effect%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20suggests%20that%20people%20are%20reluctant%20to%20help%20out%20in%20emergency%20situations%20if%20others%20are%20nearby.%20This%20theory%20dates%20back%20to%201964%2C%20when%20a%20woman%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20in%20the%20early%20morning%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20reported%20that%2038%20people%20witnessed%20the%20attack%2C%20without%20intervening.%20According%20to%20the%20bystander%20effect%2C%20the%20more%20people%20that%20witness%20an%20event%2C%20the%20less%20likely%20a%20person%20is%20to%20intervene%2C%20since%20responsibility%20becomes%20more%20diffused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20theories%20and%20studies%20from%20the%201960s%20and%201970s%20implied%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cevil%E2%80%9D%20sides%20of%20our%20character%20lie%20just%20below%20our%20civilised%20surface%2C%20while%20the%20moral%20and%20altruistic%20side%20is%20a%20thin%20veneer.%20They%20encouraged%20a%20view%20that%20human%20beings%20are%20essentially%20callous%20and%20selfish.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20findings%20of%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.st-andrews.ac.uk%2Farchive%2Fresearchers-call-for-open-and-respectful-debate-around-stanford-prison-experiment%2F%5C%22%3Eexperiments%20have%20now%20been%20contested%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20even%20discredited%20by%20other%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgen.medium.com%2Fthe-lifespan-of-a-lie-d869212b1f62%5C%22%3ERecent%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fetheses.whiterose.ac.uk%2F32348%2F1%2FAnderson_205052450_CorrectedThesisClean.pdf%5C%22%3Ecruelty%20of%20Zimbardo%E2%80%99s%20prison%20guards%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn%E2%80%99t%20emerge%20spontaneously%3B%20some%20behaviour%20was%20encouraged.%20Some%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprisoners%E2%80%9D%20later%20admitted%20that%20they%20were%20pretending%20to%20be%20distressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20a%20study%20published%20in%202007%20found%20that%20the%201964%20incident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F17874896%2F%5C%22%3Ethat%20inspired%20the%20theory%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%3Cbr%3E%5Cnbystander%20effect%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffee.org%2Farticles%2Fthe-bystander-effect-myth-or-fact%2F%5C%22%3Edistorted%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20paper%2C%20archive%20material%20shows%20far%20fewer%20people%20witnessed%20the%20incident%20than%20was%20reported%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20some%20people%20could%20only%20hear%20screams%2C%20without%20seeing%20the%20location%20of%20the%20incident.%20At%20least%20one%20person%20did%20try%20to%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20research%20indicates%20that%20bystanders%20are%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20intervene%20than%20the%20theory%20suggests.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsycnet.apa.org%2FdoiLanding%3Fdoi%3D10.1037%252Famp0000469%5C%22%3E2019%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20219%20violent%20situations%20from%20cities%20around%20the%20world%20caught%20on%20CCTV%20showed%20that%20bystanders%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20one%2C%20usually%20several%20%E2%80%93%20intervened%20to%20help%20victims%2090%25%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20that%20the%20more%20people%20were%20present%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20passers-by%20were%20to%20intervene.%20In%20the%20words%20of%20the%20study%E2%80%99s%20lead%20researcher%2C%20Richard%20Philpot%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20shows%20that%20people%20have%20a%20natural%20inclination%20to%20help%20when%20they%20see%20someone%20in%20need.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeroism%20and%20altruism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20burgeoning%20field%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscholarship.richmond.edu%2Fheroism-science%2F%5C%22%3Eheroism%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20also%20questions%20the%20bystander%20effect.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fhow-the-manchester-arena-attack-showed-that-altruism-is-human-instinct-204430%5C%22%3Erecent%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20The%20Conversation%2C%20I%20described%20how%20acts%20of%20heroic%20altruism%20are%20common%20during%20terrorist%20attacks%2C%20when%20people%20often%20risk%20their%20own%20lives%20to%20help%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20the%20following%20situation%3A%20you%E2%80%99re%20standing%20on%20a%20train%20platform.%20The%20person%20next%20to%20you%20suddenly%20faints%20and%20falls%20on%20to%20the%20track%2C%20unconscious.%20In%20the%20distance%2C%20you%20can%20see%20a%20train%20approaching.%20What%20would%20you%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20doubt%20whether%20you%20would%20act%20heroically.%20But%20don%E2%80%99t%3Cbr%3E%5Cnunderestimate%20yourself.%20There%20is%20a%20strong%20possibility%20that%2C%20before%20you%20knew%20it%2C%20you%20would%20find%20yourself%20on%20down%20on%20the%20track%2C%20helping%20the%20person%20to%20safety.%20There%20is%20a%20growing%20awareness%20amongst%20researchers%20that%20heroism%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.plos.org%2Fplosone%2Farticle%3Fid%3D10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0109687%5C%22%3Enatural%20and%20spontaneous%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6449723%2F%5C%22%3Eno%20means%20exceptional%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FlokQ9cNqAV8%3Fwmode%3Dtransparent%26start%3D0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22260%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20%E2%80%9Cperson%20jumps%20down%20on%20to%20train%20track%20to%20save%20life%E2%80%9D%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20dozens%20of%20cases%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20some%20moving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ_XU37ZArmo%5C%22%3Evideo%20footage%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlokQ9cNqAV8%5C%22%3Erecent%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20New%20York%20City%20subway%2C%20when%20a%20wheelchair-bound%20man%20fell%20on%20to%20the%20track.%20A%20bystander%20jumps%20down%2C%20pushes%20the%20wheelchair%20to%20one%20side%2C%20and%20hauls%20the%20man%20up%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20others%20on%20the%20platform.%20A%20train%20arrived%20ten%20seconds%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D72-obuscJ-E%5C%22%3EAnother%20dramatic%20video%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnshows%20an%20incident%20in%202015%2C%20when%20a%20cyclist%20was%20trapped%20under%20the%20wheel%20of%20a%20doubledecker%20bus%20in%20London.%20A%20crowd%20of%20around%20100%20people%20gathered%2C%20and%20lifted%20the%20bus.%20According%20to%20a%20paramedic%20who%20treated%20the%20man%2C%20this%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmiracle%E2%80%