E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20only%20now%20getting%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20brutal%20manner%20in%20which%20two%20Kuki%20women%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Ewere%20stripped%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20paraded%20naked%2C%20and%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3Ewas%20raped%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20a%20Meitei%20mob%2C%20according%20to%20a%20first%20information%20report%20on%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20police%20were%20aware%20of%20this%20heinous%20crime%20but%20prioritised%20personal%20sectarian%20interests%20over%20the%20course%20of%20justice.%20The%20video%20and%20public%20reactions%20force%20one%20to%20critically%20engage%20with%20the%20causes%20and%20consequences%20of%20the%20brutal%20horrors%20and%20nightmarish%20agony%20that%20locals%20have%20had%20to%20experience%20for%20the%20past%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20alarming%20about%20the%20frightful%20incident%20of%20May%204%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Ffrom-guardians-to-perpetrators-of-violence-role-of-the-meira-paibis-in-manipur%23read-more%5C%22%3EMeira%20Paibis%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20key%20participants%20in%20fuelling%20mob%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20These%20elderly%20women%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%20are%20historically%20heralded%20as%20protectors%20of%20communities%20against%20%E2%80%9Canti-social%E2%80%9D%20elements%20and%20famed%20for%20their%20spectacular%20revolt%20against%20the%20military%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20hostile%20climate%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Kuki%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20that%20were%20paraded%20as%20receptacles%20of%20communal%20identity%2C%20and%20savagely%20violated%20by%20the%20miscreants%20of%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202004%2C%20Meira%20Paibis%20gained%20international%20atten