eral%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20after%20the%20violent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepolisproject.com%2Fread%2Fmanipurs-long-wait-for-justice-remembering-1528-cases-and-the-murder-of-thangjam-manorama%2F%5C%22%3Erape%20and%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-others%2Fmanorama-rape-and-murder-10-years-on-familys-hope-for-justice-fades%2F%5C%22%3Edeath%20of%20Manorama%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20some%20reaction%20from%20the%20national%20media%2C%20but%20even%20that%20was%20not%20enough%20to%20affect%20legislative%20changes.%20The%20state%20police%20were%20aware%20of%20this%20heinous%20crime%20but%20prioritised%20personal%20sectarian%20interests%20over%20the%20course%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clear%20distinction%20though%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fwomen-of-the-northeast-present-a-picture-of-contrasts%5C%22%3EMeira%20Paibis%3C%2Fa%3E%20acted%20with%20agency%20and%20consented%20to%20the%20use%20of%20their%20body%20to%20articulate%20resistance%20against%20the%20state%20machinery.%20For%20those%20Kuki%20women%2C%20it%20was%20a%20gross%20violation%20of%20their%20bodies%20and%20psyche%20that%20was%20intentionally%20undertaken%20to%20inflict%20trauma%20and%20humiliation.%20As%20an%20act%20of%20subversion%20or%20an%20act%20of%20violation%2C%20the%20locus%20of%20aggressive%20identity%20politics%20is%20enacted%20on%20the%20naked%20woman%E2%80%99s%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20against%20women%20shows%20a%20familiar%20pattern%20of%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20a%20mob%20forcefully%20entered%20a%20party%20taking%20place%20in%20Utlou%2C%20Manipur%20and%20singled%20out%20the%20women%20(regardless%20of%20their%20community)%2C%20paraded%20them%2C%20stripped%20them%2C%20and%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20this%20distressing%20spectacle%20were%20widely%20circulated.%20But%20this%20grotesque%20incident%20did%20not%20shake%20the%20public%20consciousness%2C%20perhaps%20because%20the%20public%20stripping%20and%20parading%20of%20women%20was%20not%20dishonourable%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeira%20Paibis%20forced%20their%20way%20into%20a%20private%20house%20party%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20dishonouring%20Manipuri%20culture.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20women%20who%20were%20dragged%20out%2C%20it%20was%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20skirts%20that%20were%20tugged%2C%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20that%20were%20slapped%20and%20policed%20for%20drinking%20alcohol%20and%20wearing%20short%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20name%20of%20upholding%20culture%2C%20it%20was%20the%20women%20who%20faced%20the%20wrath%20of%20these%20gatekeepers%20of%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20%E2%80%98honour%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98dishonour%E2%80%99%2C%20encapsulated%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%2C%20is%20intensified%20in%20times%20of%20conflict.%20Rapes%20of%20women%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cother%20community%E2%80%9D%20is%20lauded%20as%20a%20righteous%20course%20of%20action%2C%20to%20fulfill%20a%20self-aggrandising%20idea%20of%20punitive%20action.%20This%20notion%20hinges%20upon%20the%20act%20of%20%E2%80%98dishonouring%E2%80%99%20or%20humiliating%20the%20other%20community.%20It%20is%20the%20sordid%20escalation%20of%20consistently%20dehumanising%20another%20community%2C%20of%20seeing%20the%20%E2%80%9Cother%E2%80%9D%20as%20an%20abject%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20legal%20and%20political%20dignitaries%20continue%20to%20debate%20the%20contours%20of%20indigeneity%2C%20the%20extent%20of%20affirmative%20action%20that%20the%20other%20community%20benefits%20from%2C%20it%20is%20civilians%20who%20burn%20in%20the%20ensuing%20crossfires.%20And%20it%20is%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20that%20bear%20the%20marks%20of%20that%20confrontation.%20Even%20in%20the%20media%20reactions%2C%20the%20treatment%20has%20been%20steeped%20in%20patriarchal%20undertones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20incident%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20shame%E2%80%9D%2C%20inappropriate%20for%20any%20civilised%20society.%20This%20is%20the%20moment%20that%20invokes%20the%20paternal%20protection%20of%20the%20state%20as%20if%20earlier%20cries%20for%20peace%20and%20help%20amid%20atrocious%20mob%20violence%20did%20not%20warrant%20enough%20attention.%20It%20is%20only%20the%20notion%20of%20shame%2C%20of%20public%20humiliation%20that%20has%20elicited%20a%20response%20of%20deep%20remorse%20from%20all%20communities%2C%20finally%20uniting%20people%20in%20horror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20last%2C%20we%20have%20earned%20the%20attention%20and%20words%20of%20condemnation%20from%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20legacy%20of%20systemic%20apathy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20apathy%20and%20political%20inertia%20to%20the%20harrowing%20accounts%20from%20Manipur%20is%20a%20disturbingly%20familiar%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Anna%20Hazare%E2%80%99s%2012-day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2011%2Faug%2F28%2Fanna-hazare-ends-hunger-strike%5C%22%3Ehunger%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20was%20widely%20telecast%20on%20national%20television.%20In%20real%20time%2C%20his%20anti-corruption%20campaign%20resonated%20with%20the%20entire%20nation%20and%20an%20outraged%2C%20mobilised%20public%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20parliament%20to%20swiftly%20make%20policy%20interventions.%20And%20yet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftracking-irom-sharmila-fasting-seeking-votes-lift-afspa-manipur%5C%22%3EIrom%20Sharmila%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20woman%20from%20Manipur%20who%20was%20on%20a%20hunger%20strike%20since%202000%2C%20received%20no%20public%20sympathy%20for%20her%20campaign%20to%20repeal%20the%20draconian%20AFSPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2Firom-sharmila-PTI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22948%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2Firom-sharmila-PTI.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2Firom-sharmila-PTI-300x182.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2Firom-sharmila-PTI-80x50.jpg%2080w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-56939%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipuri%20activist%20Irom%20Sharmila%20who%20has%20decided%20to%20break%20her%20long%20fast%20of%2016%20years.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20holds%20a%20record%20for%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20longest%20hunger%20strike%20of%2016%20years%20%E2%80%93%20she%20was%20lauded%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Iron%20lady%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20national%20outrage%20about%20the%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20provides%20unparalleled%20%E2%80%9Cspecial%E2%80%9D%20powers%20and%20legal%20impunity%20to%20military%20forces%20when%20either%20the%20state%20or%20the%20Centre%20declares%20places%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdisturbed%20areas%E2%80%9D.%20Empowered%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20judicial%20scrutiny%2C%20the%20law%20shields%20military%20forces%20from%20the%20human%20rights%20abuse%20and%20sexual%20violence%20that%20is%20unleashed%20even%20in%20cases%20of%20mere%20suspicion%20of%20militant%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20law%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmodi-govt-decides-to-reduce-disturbed-areas-under-afspa-in-northeast-amit-shah%2Farticle66660544.ece%5C%22%3Ewas%20reduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20limited%20districts%20in%20Assam%2C%20Manipur%2C%20and%20Nagaland.%20But%20the%20culture%20of%20impunity%20remains.%20It%20is%20this%20practice%20of%20legal%20and%20social%20impunity%20that%20entitles%20miscreants%20to%20engage%20in%20reprehensible%20actions%20and%20not%20fear%20legal%20or%20official%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESustained%20systemic%20practices%20of%20impunity%20have%20bred%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20utter%20distrust%20in%20legal%20and%20administrative%20justice.%20Systemic%20apathy%2C%20therefore%2C%20has%20cultivated%20a%20notion%20that%20the%20law%20does%20not%20work%2C%20or%20that%20one%20must%20go%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20law%20to%20combat%20the%20challenges%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecades%20of%20declaring%20these%20places%20as%20%E2%80%98lawless%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98disturbed%E2%80%99%20has%20only%20driven%20scant%20appreciation%20for%20legal%20mechanisms%20as%20communities%20turn%20to%20their%20own%20ways%20to%20secure%20their%20own%20interests%20and%20safety.%20It%20is%20the%20legacy%20of%20this%20systemic%20apathy%20that%20the%20sight%20of%20people%20running%20in%20fear%2C%20the%20plundering%20of%20homes%20and%20burning%20of%20vehicles%2C%20the%20needless%20deaths%20and%20countless%20vile%20conspiracies%20labelling%20entire%20communities%20as%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20militant%20groups%20could%20not%20stir%20any%20state%20or%20national%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20do%20we%20go%20from%20here%3F%20The%20state%20is%20ripped%20apart%20into%20fault%20lines%20of%20ethnically%20segregated%20neighbourhoods%20and%20there%20is%20a%20total%20breakdown%20of%20public%20trust.%20This%20collapse%20of%20communication%20and%20mutual%20support%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20only%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20crumbling%20away%20of%20trust%20in%20electoral%20leaders%20at%20both%20the%20federal%20and%20the%20Union%20level.%20It%20affects%20the%20larger%20region%20which%20is%20home%20to%20several%20other%20communities%20and%20how%20they%20witness%20the%20fallout%20of%20this%20conflict.%20It%20is%20the%20self-fulfilling%20prophecy%20that%20labelled%20the%20region%20as%20%E2%80%98disturbed%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98lawless%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20did%20nothing%20as%20the%20hours%20of%20burnings%2C%20displacements%20and%20ceasefires%20protracted%20into%20days%2C%20and%20extended%20into%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20the%20delayed%20circulation%20of%20a%20gruesome%20video%20of%20sexual%20assault%20to%20jolt%20people%2C%20to%20catch%20national%20attention.%20And%20the%20reason%20we%20are%20only%20hearing%20of%20this%20outrage%20now%20is%20because%20there%20is%20a%20complete%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20on%20the%20premise%20that%20the%20ban%20will%20stop%20the%20spread%20of%20fake%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20fake%20news%20continued%20to%20be%20spread%20and%20communal%20tension%20was%20incessantly%20stoked%20regardless%20of%20the%20internet%20ban.%20Ironically%2C%20it%20could%20only%20be%20with%20the%20use%20of%20the%20internet%20that%20the%20case%20has%20come%20to%20light%20and%20some%20semblance%20of%20remedial%20action%20has%20been%20possible.%20But%20by%20making%20the%20conversation%20about%20tribal%20and%20non-tribal%20identities%2C%20religious%20differences%2C%20and%20by%20laying%20contested%20claims%20to%20indigeneity%20and%20citizenship%2C%20the%20core%20issue%20remains%20unresolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20strife%20is%20the%20question%20of%20claims%20to%20affirmative%20action%20for%20education%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20resources.%20Restoring%20peace%20in%20the%20state%20requires%20acknowledgment%20and%20redressal%20of%20these%20deep-seated%20concerns%20and%20a%20clear%20commitment%20to%20the%20protection%20of%20all%20legal%20residents.%20Perhaps%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20nation%20cannot%20see%20our%20grief%20and%20finds%20the%20ethnic%20divisions%20too%20banal%20for%20its%20attention.%20It%20will%20be%20up%20to%20our%20local%20communities%20to%20foster%20hope%20and%20reparation%20to%20build%20a%20better%20future%20than%20our%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESainico%20Ningthoujam%20is%20a%20doctoral%20scholar%20and%20Tomlinson%20Fellow%20at%20McGill%20University%2C%20Canada.%20Her%20research%20focusses%20on%20climate%20narratives%2C%20gender%20and%20post-colonial%20studies.%20She%20is%20a%20former%20Zubaan-Sasakawa%20Peace%20Foundation%20research%20grant%20awardee%20and%20a%20former%20Sahapedia%E2%80%93UNESCO%20Fellow.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690368349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F05112619%2FFxU5VuNXgAIhwAS.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fin-manipur-violence-against-women-impunity-and-apathy-show-a-familiar-pattern-of-events%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22But%20why%20is%20only%20the%20graphic%20revolting%20image%20of%20naked%20women%20that%20attracts%20public%20attention%20to%20regions%20that%20are%20deemed%20too%20remote%20and%20peripheral%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fin-manipur-violence-against-women-impunity-and-apathy-show-a-familiar-pattern-of-events%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tech%20Mahindra%20Q1FY24%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20falls%2038.8%25%20YoY%20to%20Rs%20692.5%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690367526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fhp%2Fhome-page%2F2021-04%2F26%2Ffull%2F1619434290-2884.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ftech-mahindra-q1fy24-results-net-profit-falls-38-8-yoy-to-rs-692-5-crore-123072600552_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20quarter%2C%20the%20company's%20headcount%20stood%20at%20148%2C297.%20It%20was%20down%204%2C103%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20March%20quarter%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ftech-mahindra-q1fy24-results-net-profit-falls-38-8-yoy-to-rs-692-5-crore-123072600552_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%20Two-Thirds%20of%20Hospitals%20Under%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Scheme%20Active%20Now%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F30121127%2Fayushman-bharat-digital-mission.png%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20More%20than%20a%20third%20of%20hospitals%20empanelled%20under%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20are%20inactive%2C%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fover-a-third-of-hospitals-empanelled-under-ayushman-bharat-scheme-in-new-delhi-are-inactive-official-data-11690305764552.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20studying%20official%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20this%20data%20is%20updated%20daily%20and%20at%20present%2C%2018%2C783%20out%20of%20the%2027%2C000%20hospitals%20under%20the%20scheme%20are%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(PM-JAY)%20has%20been%20touted%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnha.gov.in%2FPM-JAY%5C%22%3Ethe%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20health%20assurance%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20aims%20to%20provide%20health%20cover%20of%20Rs.%205%20lakhs%20per%20family%20per%20year%20for%20secondary%20and%20tertiary%20care%20hospitalisation%20to%20over%2012%20crores%20poor%20and%20vulnerable%20families%2C%20covering%20approximately%2055%20crore%20beneficiaries%20that%20form%20the%20bottom%2040%25%20of%20the%20Indian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20households%20included%20are%20based%20on%20the%20deprivation%20and%20occupational%20criteria%20of%20Socio-Economic%20Caste%20Census%202011%20(SECC%202011)%20for%20rural%20and%20urban%20areas%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said%20that%204%2C682%20hospitals%20had%20been%20inactive%20since%202018%2C%20when%20the%20scheme%20was%20introduced%2C%20and%20had%20not%20served%20a%20single%20scheme%20beneficiary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20as%20many%20as%203%2C632%20hospitals%20only%20turned%20inactive%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months.%20It%20is%20not%20mentioned%20if%20this%20sudden%20surge%20was%20due%20to%20delayed%20tallying%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20insurance%20scheme%20was%20just%20one%20component%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%20The%20other%20had%20promised%20the%20creation%20of%201%2C50%2C000%20health%20and%20wellness%20centres%20(HWCs)%20by%20transforming%20the%20existing%20sub-centres%20and%20primary%20health%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690366862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F30121127%2Fayushman-bharat-digital-mission.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fayushman-bharat-scheme-inactive-hospitals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20'Mint'%20report%20said%20that%204%2C682%20hospitals%20out%20of%20the%2027%2C000%20originally%20empanelled%2C%20had%20been%20inactive%20since%202018%2C%20when%20the%20scheme%20was%20introduced%2C%20and%20had%20not%20served%20a%20single%20scheme%20beneficiary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fayushman-bharat-scheme-inactive-hospitals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Names%20of%20More%20Than%205%20Crore%20Deleted%20From%20MGNREGS%20in%20FY%202022-23%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07101954%2F7655150258_021e6c9ffd_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20State%20governments%20across%20the%20country%20have%20deleted%20the%20names%20of%205.18%20crore%20workers%20registered%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme%20(MGNREGS)%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202022-2023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20represents%20a%20247%25%20increase%20in%20deletions%20compared%20to%20the%20last%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20rural%20development%20minister%20Giriraj%20Singh%20provided%20these%20statistics%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F661244349%2FJuly-25-reply-by-Ministry-of-Rural-Development-on-MGNREGS-deletions%5C%22%3Ewritten%20reply%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2025%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20reply%20stated%20that%20there%20were%20many%20reasons%20for%20the%20deletions%2C%20including%20%E2%80%9C1.%20fake%20job%20card%20(incorrect%20job%20card)%2C%202.%20duplicate%20job%20card%2C%203.%20now%20not%20willing%20to%20work%2C%204.%20family%20shifted%20from%20gram%20panchayat%20permanently%2C%20and%205.%20single%20person%20in%20job%20card%20and%20the%20person%20is%20expired%20%5Bsic%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20by%20Congress%20MPs%20V.K.%20Sreekandan%20and%20Gourav%20Gogoi%20asking%20if%20it%20was%20true%20that%20over%20a%20crore%20names%20had%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20MGNREGS%20system%2C%20and%20if%20so%2C%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MGNREGS%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20employment%20to%20rural%20households%20in%20the%20country%20at%20specially%20notified%20minimum%20wages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWork%20under%20the%20scheme%20involves%20physical%20labour%20and%20includes%20activities%20such%20as%20construction%2C%20afforestation%20and%20land-levelling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20clarified%20in%20his%20response%20that%20%E2%80%9Csys