%20football%20will%20shine%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeavy%20investment%20and%20a%20coaching%20group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Moroccan%20Football%20Association%20has%20invested%20in%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20game%20since%202009%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20rapid%20transformation%20since%20president%20Fouzi%20Lekjaa%20kickstarted%20a%20four-year%20plan%20in%202020%20with%20support%20from%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20monarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20professionalized%20the%20top%20two%20divisions%2C%20provided%20set%20minimum%20wages%20for%20players%20and%20the%20staff%20of%20all%20clubs%2C%20and%20bolstered%20grassroots%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHiring%20Reynald%20Pedros%20was%20another%20masterstroke.%20The%20French%20coach%20won%20two%20women%E2%80%99s%20Champions%20League%20titles%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwomens-champions-league-lyon-retake-european-throne-on-night-of-historic-support%2Fa-61890010%5C%22%3Epowerhouses%20Olympique%20Lyon%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20quickly%20reshaped%20the%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPedros%20introduced%C2%A0training%20standards%20and%C2%A0tactics%20and%20player%20confidence%20rose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20achievements%20are%20the%20result%20of%20continuous%20work%20over%20the%20years.%20We%20had%20big%20ambitions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chebbak%20said.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%E2%80%99re%20concentrating%20on%20the%20World%20Cup.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorocco%20will%20rely%20on%20foreign-born%20talent%20with%20Moroccan%20roots%20at%20this%20tournament%20with%20Rosella%20Ayane%20(England)%2C%20Yasmin%20Mrabet%20(Spain)%20and%20Elodie%20Nakkach%20(France)%20playing%20vital%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20professionalisation%20of%20the%20domestic%20leagues%20should%20be%20the%20bedrock%20for%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShifting%20opinions%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20sport%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChabbak%20was%20fortunate%20that%20her%20family%20were%20always%20supportive%20of%20her%20dream%20to%20play%20professional%20football%2C%20particularly%20her%20father%2C%20Larbi%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20national%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20football-loving%20family%20who%20supported%20and%20advised%20me.%20My%20father%20always%20provided%20me%20with%20guidance%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThankfully%2C%20I%20can%20say%20that%20I%20made%20him%20proud%20and%20I%20want%20to%20make%20him%20even%20prouder.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20weren%E2%80%99t%20so%20fortunate%2C%20facing%20opposition%20from%20their%20community%20and%20even%20their%20own%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20lost%20many%20talents%20due%20to%20societal%20views%20and%20families%E2%80%99%20rejection%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chebbak%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20many%20talented%20players%20who%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20go%20far.%20But%20families%20were%20afraid%20of%20allowing%20their%20daughters%20to%20play%20football%20and%20prevented%20them%20from%20doing%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGermany%20are%20Morocco%E2%80%99s%20first%20opponents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20so%20proud%20to%20witness%20these%20achievements%20and%20see%20Morocco%20contribute%20to%20the%20growth%20and%20recognition%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bouchti%2C%20who%20travelled%20to%20Melbourne%20to%20attend%20the%20opener%20against%20Germany.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20want%20to%20thank%20them%20for%20raising%20our%20flag%20and%20making%20us%20very%20proud.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20H%20isn%E2%80%99t%20set%20to%20get%20much%20easier%20with%20games%20against%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-cup-casey-phair-makes-south-korean-football-history%2Fa-66294107%5C%22%3ESouth%20Korea%20and%20Colombia%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20confidence%20running%20through%20this%20team%20should%20help%20them%20achieve%20their%20lofty%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20incredible%20to%20qualify%20but%20now%20our%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chebbak%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20it%20will%20be%20challenging%20but%20we%20will%20concentrate%20on%20our%20style%20of%20play.%20We%20want%20to%20be%20competitive%20and%20reach%20the%20second%20round.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Morocco%E2%80%99s%20meteoric%20rise%20in%20football%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20their%20ambitions%20appear%20within%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fmoroccos-womens-world-cup-team-reaps-investment-rewards%2Fa-66283907%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690366201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26153718%2FUntitled-design-9.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fhow-moroccos-passion-for-football-is-flowing-into-the-womens-world-cup%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Investment%20in%20women's%20soccer%20is%20paying%20off%20for%20Morocco%2C%20who%20are%20competing%20at%20their%20first%20Women's%20World%20Cup.%20Captain%20Ghizlane%20Chebbak%20says%20public%20support%20is%20pushing%20the%20team%20forward.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fhow-moroccos-passion-for-football-is-flowing-into-the-womens-world-cup%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BPCL%20Q1FY24%20result%3A%20Net%20profit%20at%20Rs%2010%2C644.30%20cr%3B%20revenue%20down%20by%207.3%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690365518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.busin