A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Amalapuram%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Raju%20worked%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20for%20several%20years%20in%20the%20US.%20In%202012%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20as%20the%20global%20delivery%20head%20of%20a%20large%20firm%20to%20pursue%20his%20entrepreneurial%20dream.%20This%20journey%20began%20with%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20that%20he%20ran%20till%202017.%20After%20selling%20it%20that%20year%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20food%20and%20nutrition%20were%20two%20areas%20he%20wanted%20to%20continue%20to%20focus%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20how%20Hyderabad-based%20Troo%20Good%2C%20a%20millet%20snack%20company%2C%20was%20formed%20in%202018.%20It%20sells%20around%202%20million%20millet%20%3Cem%3Echikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eper%20day%2C%20and%20is%20on%20track%20to%20achieve%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20millet%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChikki%3A%20India%E2%80%99s%20nutri-bars%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chikkis%20being%20made%20at%20a%20Troo%20Good%20facility%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325146%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChikkis%20being%20made%20at%20one%20of%20Troo%20Good%E2%80%99s%20manufacturing%20facilities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20food%20affordable%2C%20I%20needed%20something%20locally%20available.%20Quinoa%20is%20a%20good%2C%20healthy%20alternative%20to%20wheat%2C%20but%20it%20is%20expensive%20and%20has%20to%20be%20imported.%20Then%20I%20found%20millets%2C%20which%20are%20the%20best%20choice.%20They%20are%20as%20economical%20as%20wheat%2C%20but%20much%20more%20nutritious%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Organization%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20(FAO)%20says%20that%20millets%20provide%20antioxidants%2C%20minerals%2C%20fibre%2C%20iron%20and%20protein%2C%20alongside%20being%20gluten-free%20with%20a%20low-glycaemic%20index.%20Millets%20are%20also%20economical%20as%20they%20require%20less%20water%20and%20fewer%20pesticides%2C%20and%20are%20also%20climate%20resilient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20explains%20that%20he%20began%20his%20journey%20with%20selling%20millet%20parathas%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20the%20same%20taste%20and%20higher%20nutrition%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20normal%20wheat-based%20paratha%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20selling%20Hello%20Curry%2C%20I%20started%20selling%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20%3C%2Fem%3Eparathas%20to%20local%20schools%20and%20corporations%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2047-year-old%2C%20adding%20that%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20demand%20eventually%20became%20an%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20began%20with%20selling%201%2C000%20parathas%20a%20month%2C%20he%20scaled%20up%20to%2090%2C000%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20three%20months.%20However%2C%20another%20challenge%20was%20the%20short%20shelf%20life%20of%20the%20parathas%2C%20alongside%20the%20fact%20that%20Raju%E2%80%99s%20venture%20was%20bootstrapped.%