xisting%20options%20only%20cater%20to%20taste.%20I%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20three%20fundamentals%20through%20Troo%20Good%20%E2%80%94%20affordability%2C%20taste%20and%20nutrition.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20millet%20parathas%20were%20already%20such%20a%20hit%2C%20he%20started%20working%20on%20how%20the%20grains%20could%20be%20turned%20into%20snacks.%20He%20then%20found%20the%20%3Cem%3Echikki%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20is%20known%20to%20have%20a%20higher%20shelf%20life%2C%20to%20be%20a%20perfect%20vessel%20to%20help%20him%20with%20his%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20in-house%20team%20of%20scientists%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314758%2Fmothers-start-rigdam-foods-ready-to-eat-millet-snacks-for-children-earn-turnover-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformulated%20the%20millet%20%3Cem%3Echikki%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20contains%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20peanuts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20improved%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20this%20%3Cem%3Echikki%3C%2Fem%3E%20due%20to%20food%20fortification.%20Food%20fortification%20is%20the%20practice%20of%20adding%20essential%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%20to%20commonly%20consumed%20foods%20during%20processing%20to%20increase%20their%20nutritional%20value%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20A%20Laxmaiah%2C%20former%20scientist%20G%20(Director%20Grade%20Scientist)%20%26amp%3B%20head%2C%20Division%20of%20Public%20Health%20Nutrition%3B%20head%20Research%20and%20Development%20and%20Quality%2C%20Troo%20Good.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHiring%2C%20producing%2C%20and%20selling%20locally%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2280%20percent%20of%20Troo%20Good's%20factory%20employees%20are%20women%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325157%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEighty%20percent%20of%20Troo%20Good%E2%80%99s%20factory%20employees%20are%20women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20%3C%2Fem%3E(NFHS-5)%202019-21%2C%20undernutrition%20remains%20a%20big%20problem%20among%20children.%20If%20we%20take%20the%20example%20of%20Chattisgarh%2C%20the%20survey%20found%20that%2031.3%25%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%205%20are%20underweight%20and%2034.6%25%20are%20stunted.%20The%20study%20also%20found%20that%20girls%2C%20women%2C%20and%20young%20mothers%20are%20anaemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTroo%20Good%E2%80%99s%20millet%20%3Cem%3Echikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20protein%2C%20iron%2C%20and%20beta-carotene.%20For%20children%2C%20the%20consumption%20of%20this%20wondergrain%20helps%20battle%20deficiency%20diseases%20like%20Bitot%E2%80%99s%20spots%2C%20night%20blindness%2C%20corneal%20ulcers%2C%20keratomalacia%2C%20anaemia%2C%20and%20helps%20in%20growth%20and%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20A%20Laxmaiah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETroo%20Good%20sells%20these%20%3Cem%3Echikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20schools%20across%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20are%20dealing%20with%20a%20major%20issue%20of%20malnutrition.%20I%20found%20that%20millets%20could%20be%20a%20panacea%20for%20solving%20the%20nutrition%20issue%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raju%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20first%20began%20their%20operations%20in%202018%2C%20Troo%20Good%20started%20by%20selling%20100%20kg%20a%20day.%20In%20September%2C%20a%20sudden%20uptick%20in%20demand%20meant%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20produce%20at%20least%205%2C000%20kg%20a%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20outsource%20our%20production%2C%20so%20scaling%20was%20a%20huge%20challenge%20for%20us.%20I%20believe%20in%20hiring%20locals%2C%20procuring%20raw%20material%20locally%2C%20producing%20locally%20and%20selling%20locally.%20Suddenly%20a%20tsunami%20hit%20us%20in%20terms%20of%20demand%20and%20we%20were%20not%20prepared.%20We%20just%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20infrastructure.%20We%20needed%20to%20add%20at%20least%20three%20new%20factories%20in%2010%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Raju.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20this%2C%20he%20booked%20buses%20and%20sent%20his%20employees%20to%20remote%20places%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20nearby%20states.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20needed%20skilled%20manpower.%20My%20team%20members%20went%20to%20villages%20and%20spent%20nights%20in%20the%20houses%20of%20contractors.%20We%20had%20to%20add%20factories%20at%20lightning%20speed.%20With%20a%20ton%20of%20courage%2C%20we%20added%20three%20factories%20in%2015%20days%20and%20increased%20our%20volumes%20to%205%2C000%20kgs%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20CEO%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20then%20scaled%20to%2030%2C000%20kg%2C%20and%20so%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20adds%20that%20by%20producing%20themselves%2C%20they%20are%20able%20to%20have%20higher%20margins%2C%20as%20well%20as%20provide%20employment.%20They%20have%20five%20manufacturing%20facilities%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Chattisgarh.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWith%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%2053%20crore%20in%20FY%202022-23%2C%20they%20are%20on%20track%20to%20achieve%20a%20Rs%20100%20crore%20revenue%20in%20this%20financial%20year%2C%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20have%20sold%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271562%2Fchennai-woman-sells-ready-to-eat-snack-mixes-from-ancient-grains%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E40%20crore%20millet%20%3Cem%3Echikkis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eso%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20aid%20in%20operations%2C%20they%20also%20hire%20locally%20and%20work%20with%20self-help%20groups%2C%20with%2080%25%20of%20their%20factory%20workers%20being%20women%2C%20according%20to%20Raju.%20%E2%80%9CWherever%20we%20go%2C%20we%20train%20the%20women%20at%20the%20self-help%20groups.%20We%20also%20help%20farmers%20by%20directly%20buying%20from%20them%2C%20helping%20them%20increase%20their%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20water%2C%20one%20%3Cem%3Echikki%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Troo%20Good%20has%20sold%2040%20crore%20millet%20chikkis%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325161%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETroo%20Good%20has%20sold%2040%20crore%20millet%20chikkis%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20currently%20working%20with%20the%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Chattisgarh%20state%20governments%20on%20multiple%20initiatives%20including%20child%20welfare%2C%20young%20mothers%20welfare%20and%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20scheme.%20They%20have%20also%20tied%20up%20with%20The%20Akshaya%20Patra%20Foundation%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Vedanta%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20supplement%20nutrition%20in%20the%20Anganwadis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20farm%20to%20fork%20approach%2C%20the%20company%20works%20with%20about%2015%2C000%20farmers%20in%20these%20states%20directly.%20Raju%20says%20that%20Troo%20Good%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277456%2Fmillet-man-of-telangana-veer-shetty-biradar-ss-bhavani-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elargest%20purchaser%20of%20millets%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20farmer-friendly%20crops%20and%20also%20beneficial%20to%20the%20environment.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ENABARD%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%2C%20millets%20can%20be%20cultivated%20in%20areas%20that%20have%20low%20rainfall%20and%20poor%20soil%20fertility.%20The%20report%20adds%20that%20millets%20are%20tolerant%20to%20drought%20and%20have%20higher%20nutrient%20content%20compared%20to%20major%20cereal%20crops%20and%20ensure%20food%20and%20nutrition%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20says%20that%20while%20rice%20requires%20about%204%2C500%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20kg%2C%20mil